Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}(1858年）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（美国内战的二年前）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（德州的某处）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谁在黑暗中鬼鬼祟祟的？{\r}\NWho's that stumblin' around in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}报上你的目的，否则准备断臂{\r}\NState your business or prepare to get winged!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}冷静，两位 我没有恶意{\r}\NCalm yourselves, gentlemen. I mean you no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我只是同样疲倦的旅人{\r}\NI'm simply a fellow weary traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}停,马儿{\r}\NBoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}寒冷的清晨，两位{\r}\NGood cold evening, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我在找一对奴隶商名叫史佩克兄弟{\r}\NI'm looking for a pair of slave traders that go by the name of the Speck Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是你们吗？{\r}\NMight that be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 谁想知道？ - 我想{\r}\N- Who wants to know? - Well, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是金史华兹医生 这是我的马费兹{\r}\NI'm Dr. King Schultz. This is my horse, Fritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 哪门子医生？ - 牙医{\r}\N- What kinda doctor? - Dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们是史佩克兄弟吗？{\r}\NNow, are you the Speck Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们在格林维尔奴隶拍卖会中 买下那群人吗？{\r}\NAnd did you purchase those men at the Greenville slave auction?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 那又怎样？ - 我希望跟你们谈判{\r}\N- So what? - So I wish to parley with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}说英语{\r}\N- Speak English.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抱歉{\r}\N- Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请见谅，英语是我的第二语言{\r}\NPlease forgive me. It is a second language.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在你的财产中，我打听到…{\r}\NNow, amongst your inventory, I've been led to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有个我急欲获得的黑奴{\r}\Nis a specimen I'm keen to acquire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位可怜鬼好！{\r}\NHello, you poor devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们有人是来自…{\r}\NIs there one amongst you who was formerly a resident
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}卡洛肯庄园吗？{\r}\Nof the Carrucan plantation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我来自卡洛肯庄园{\r}\NI'm from the Carrucan plantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谁在说话？{\r}\NWho said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你叫什么名字？{\r}\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥{\r}\NDjango.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那你正是我在找的人{\r}\NThen you are exactly the one I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你知道毕氏兄弟是谁吗？{\r}\NDo you know who the Brittle Brothers are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们是谁？{\r}\NWho are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大约翰{\r}\NBig John.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}艾利斯{\r}\NEllis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}罗杰{\r}\NRoger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有时他们叫他小拉杰{\r}\NSometime they call him Lil Raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们是卡洛肯庄园的监工{\r}\NThey was overseers at the Carrucan plantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不再是了{\r}\NNot anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:07:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}告诉我 如果再看到他们三人{\r}\NTell me... if you were to see any of these three gentlemen again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你能认出吗？ - 喂{\r}\N- would you recognize them? - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 别那样跟他说话 - 怎样？{\r}\N- Stop talkin' to him like that. - Like What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那样{\r}\NLike that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老兄，我只是想确定…{\r}\NMy good man, I'm simply trying to ascertain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}说英语，可恶{\r}\NSpeak English, goddamn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大家冷静{\r}\NEverybody calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我只是想做生意的顾客{\r}\NI'm simply a customer trying to conduct a transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不在乎，不卖，快滚{\r}\NI don't care. No sale. Now, off with ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别傻了，他们就是要卖的{\r}\NDon't be ridiculous. Of course they're for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}走开{\r}\NMove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老兄，你只是想来个下马威{\r}\NMy good man, did you simply get carried away with your dramatic gesture
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或是你把枪指着我有杀人意图？{\r}\Nor are you pointing your weapon at me with lethal intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}最后机会，臭屁鬼{\r}\NLast chance, fancy pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很好{\r}\NOh, very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抱歉杀了你的马 但我怕你乱来{\r}\NI'm sorry to put a bullet in your beast, but I didn't want you to do anything rash
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}忘了先冷静下来{\r}\Nbefore you had a moment to come to your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你这混帐王八蛋！{\r}\NYou goddamn son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你杀了罗斯柯{\r}\N- You shot Roscoe! -
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是啊{\r}\N Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}也杀了艾斯{\r}\NAnd you killed Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谁叫他威胁射杀我{\r}\NI only shot your brother once he threatened to shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我相信我有…{\r}\NAnd I do believe I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一、二、三、四{\r}\None, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}五位证人能作证{\r}\Nfive witnesses who can attest to that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 干，我的腿断了 - 废话{\r}\N- Damn leg's busted! - No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拜托你别哭了{\r}\NNow, if you could keep your caterwauling down to a minimum,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想向决哥小伙子问完话{\r}\NI'd like to finish my line of inquiry with young Django.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}痛死了！{\r}\N- God-fuckin'-damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如我所说{\r}\N- As I was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果再看到他们三人 你能认出吗？{\r}\Nif you were to see the Brittle Brothers again, you could recognize 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可以{\r}\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}成交！{\r}\NSold American!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}怎样，史佩克先生？{\r}\NSo, Mr. Speck? Mr. Speck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史佩克先生？决哥小伙子卖多少？{\r}\NHow much for young Django here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这铁链太夭寿了{\r}\NThat iron is nasty business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拿一下好吗？{\r}\NOh, could you hold this for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThank you. Django?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥，你骑那只马{\r}\NGet up on that horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有，换作是我{\r}\NAlso, if I were you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我会拿走史佩克大哥遗留的外套{\r}\NI'd take that winter coat the dear departed Speck left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑鬼！不准碰我哥的外套{\r}\NNigger! Don't you touch my brother's coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}该死{\r}\NGoddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}100元、10元…{\r}\NOne hundred... ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}20元…{\r}\N20...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再5元{\r}\Nand five...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}买决哥小伙子{\r}\Nfor young Django here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}既然他用不着了{\r}\NAnd since he won't be needing it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想买你哥的马{\r}\NI'd like to purchase your brother's nag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有，史佩克先生{\r}\NAlso, Mr. Speck,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}恐怕我需要收据，你有吗？{\r}\NI'm afraid I will require a bill of sale. Do you have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}去死吧，牙医{\r}\NYou go to hell, dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就知道你没有{\r}\NI thought not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}放心啦，我有备而来{\r}\NNo worries. I come prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这能充当收据{\r}\NThis will serve nicely as a bill of sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}至于你们这些可怜鬼{\r}\NNow, as to you poor devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}依我看{\r}\NSo, as I see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谈到诸位的下一步{\r}\Nwhen it comes to the subject of what to do next,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们有两个选择{\r}\Nyou gentlemen have two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}第一选择{\r}\NOne:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我离开后 你们能扛着还没死的史佩克{\r}\NOnce I'm gone, you could lift that beast off the remaining Speck,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}送他到最近的城镇{\r}\Nthen carry him to the nearest town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}起码距离这里37英里{\r}\NWhich would be at least 37 miles back the way you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或是第二选择{\r}\NOr two:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们自行解开铁链{\r}\NYou could unshackle yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拿着那支枪{\r}\Ntake that rifle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}轰了他的头，把两人给埋了{\r}\Nput a bullet in his head, bury the two of them deep,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}去国内比较开化的地区{\r}\Nand then make your way to a more enlightened area of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}由你们选择{\r}\NChoice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}给个提示 要是你们有人热中天文学{\r}\NOh, and on the off chance there are any astronomy aficionados amongst you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}北极星是那颗{\r}\Nthe North Star is that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拜拜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大伙儿，等一下，有话好说{\r}\NNow wait a minute, fellas. Let's talk about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这种情况要讲道理{\r}\NYou gotta be reasonable in a situation like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不是坏人，我只是做分内事{\r}\NI'm not a bad guy. I'm just doin' my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}蓝莓，我不是把吃剩的苹果给你？{\r}\NBlueberry, didn't I give you my last apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这样吧{\r}\NTell you what, boys:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}带我去艾尔帕索看医生 我会放你们自由{\r}\NTake me to the doc in El Paso, I'll get you your freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不要，拜托{\r}\NNo. No, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（道崔镇，德州）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}听着{\r}\NAll right, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}今晚吃两颗{\r}\NI'd like you to take two of these tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}隔天早上就…{\r}\Nand then in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑鬼在骑马{\r}\NThat's a nigger on a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大家在看什么？{\r}\NWhat's everybody staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们从没看过黑人骑马{\r}\NThey ain't never seen no nigger on a horse before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}早安，客栈老板{\r}\NGood morning, innkeeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两杯啤酒给两位累坏的旅客{\r}\NTwo beers for two weary travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还太早，再一小时才营业{\r}\NIt's still a bit early. We won't be open for another hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到时会提供早餐{\r}\NBy then, we'll be servin' breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你竟敢进来{\r}\NWhat the hell you think you're doing, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}叫那黑鬼出去{\r}\NGet that nigger outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}救命！救命！ 客栈老板{\r}\N- Help! Help! - Innkeeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}记得，叫警长来，不是治安官{\r}\NRemember, get the sheriff, not the marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长！救命！{\r}\NSheriff! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真扫兴{\r}\NAlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们只能自己倒酒了{\r}\NNow we must act as our own bartender.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}坐下，老弟{\r}\NSit down, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你是哪门子牙医？{\r}\NWhat kind of dentist are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}即便有马车，我有五年没行医了{\r}\NDespite that cart, I haven't practiced dentistry in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但最近我转行了{\r}\NBut these days, I practice a new profession...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}赏金猎人{\r}\Nbounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}知道什么是赏金猎人吗？{\r}\NDo you know what a bounty hunter is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不明白{\r}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就是…{\r}\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}奴隶交易是用人命换现金{\r}\Nthe way the slave trade deals in human lives for cash,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}赏金猎人是尸体换现金{\r}\Na bounty hunter deals in corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}帽子{\r}\NHat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}干杯{\r}\NProst.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}州政府悬赏一个人头{\r}\NThe state places a bounty on a man's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我追踪那个人，找到就杀了他{\r}\NI track that man, I find that man, I kill that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然后再把尸体运回当局{\r}\NAfter I've killed him, I transport that man's corpse back to the authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有时说来容易做起来难{\r}\NSometimes that's easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我给当局尸体证明我确实杀了他{\r}\NI show that corpse to the authorities, proving yes, indeed, I truly have killed him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这时当局就会付我赏金{\r}\Nat which point the authorities pay me the bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}类似奴隶制，这一行是尸肉换现金{\r}\NSo, like slavery, it's a flesh for cash business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么是赏金？{\r}\NWhat's a bounty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}像是酬金{\r}\NIt's like a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你杀人？还有钱领？{\r}\NYou kill people? And they give you a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}杀特定对象，对{\r}\NCertain people, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}坏人{\r}\NBad people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}愈坏酬金愈高{\r}\NBadder they are, bigger the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所以我才找上你{\r}\NWhich brings me to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我得承认找你，是有点为难{\r}\NAnd I must admit, I'm at a bit of a quandary when it comes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一来我鄙视奴隶制度{\r}\NOn one hand, I despise slavery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但另一方面我还是需要你帮忙{\r}\NOn the other hand, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果你无法拒绝，更好{\r}\NIf you're not in a position to refuse, all the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}暂时我得借助你的力量来帮我{\r}\NSo, for the time being, I'm gonna make this slavery malarkey work to my benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}尽管如此{\r}\NStill, having said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我感到内疚{\r}\N I feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所以我想要我俩达成协议{\r}\NSo, I would like the two of us to enter into an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要找到毕氏兄弟{\r}\NI'm looking for the Brittle Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不过这任务对我来说有个小麻烦{\r}\NHowever, at this endeavor,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就是我不认得他们的长相{\r}\NI'm at a slight disadvantage insofar as I don't know what they look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但你认得，对吧？{\r}\NBut you do. Don't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我当然认得他们的长相{\r}\NI know what they look like all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很好{\r}\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的提案如下{\r}\NSo here's my agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你跟我同行直到找到他们{\r}\N- You travel with me until we find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们要去哪里？{\r}\N- Where we goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}听说他们至少有两人 在北边的盖特林堡当监工{\r}\NI hear at least two of them are overseeing up in Gatlinburg,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我不知道位置{\r}\Nbut I don't know where.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那表示得跑遍盖特林堡的庄园 直到找到他们{\r}\NThat means we visit every plantation in Gatlinburg till we find 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}找到他们时{\r}\NAnd when we find them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你指出他们，我杀掉他们{\r}\Nyou point them out, and I kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你愿意的话{\r}\NYou do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我同意放你自由 外加每个毕氏兄弟给25元 总共是75元{\r}\NI agree to give you your freedom, $25 per Brittle Brother. That's $75.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真准时，警长来了{\r}\NAnd, as if on cue, here comes the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好，两位，闹够了{\r}\NOK, boys. Fun's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}出来{\r}\NCome on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好，乡民，冷静{\r}\NAll right, folks, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}去忙自己的事{\r}\NGo about your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这些小丑很快会滚蛋{\r}\NThese jokers will be gone soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们为什么来我的镇惹麻烦？{\r}\NNow, why y'all wanna come into my town and start trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}吓坏了这群好人{\r}\NAnd scare all these nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们没事可干{\r}\NYou ain't got nothing better to do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只会来比尔夏普的镇{\r}\Nthan to come into Bill Sharp's town
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡搞一通？{\r}\Nand show your ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你竟然对警长开枪{\r}\NWhat'd you just do to our sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在能找治安官了{\r}\NNow you can get the marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}治安官！治安官！{\r}\NMarshal! Marshal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 要进去等吗？ - 能闪人吗？{\r}\N- Should we wait inside? - Can we just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你先请{\r}\NAfter you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:20:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把马车移到酒馆对街远一点{\r}\NMove that buckboard a long ways across the street from the saloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要六名枪手在后面{\r}\NI want six men, six rifles behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两名枪手在这边屋顶{\r}\NI want two men, two rifles up on this roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两名枪手在那边屋顶{\r}\NTwo men, two rifles on that roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所有枪都瞄准前门{\r}\NAll the barrels aimed at that front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}来人把可怜的比尔拖走{\r}\NSomebody get poor Bill outta the goddamn street.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}酒馆里的家伙！{\r}\NYou in the saloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们有一百名枪手 在各个角落瞄准那间店{\r}\NWe got a hundred rifles aimed at every way out of that buildin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们只有一个机会能活着出来{\r}\NYou got one chance to get out of this alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你和黑鬼立刻手举高出来 立刻照办{\r}\NYou and your nigger come out right now with your hands over your head, and I mean right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这位是我有幸谈话的治安官吗？{\r}\NIs this the marshal I have the pleasure of addressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没错{\r}\NYes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是美国治安官吉尔塔图{\r}\NThis is U.S. Marshal Gill Tatum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}太棒了，治安官{\r}\NNa wunderbar, marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我完全缴械了{\r}\NI have relieved myself of all weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如你所指示{\r}\Nand just as you have instructed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我准备走出去{\r}\NI am ready to step outside
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}手举高{\r}\Nwith my hands raised above my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我相信这位…{\r}\NI trust as a representative
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美国刑法制度的代表{\r}\Nof the criminal justice system of the United States of America,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不会当街射杀我{\r}\NI shan't be shot down in the street
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}无论是你或你的手下{\r}\Nby either you or your deputies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}除非我受到司法审判{\r}\Nbefore I've had my day in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你指像你对警长干的事？{\r}\NYou mean like you did our sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}像杀狗一样当街射杀他{\r}\NShot him down like a dog in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，就是这个意思{\r}\NYes, that's exactly what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}身为执法者，你能保证…{\r}\NDo I have your word as a lawman not to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不会像杀狗一样当街射杀我？{\r}\Nshoot me down like a dog in the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}虽然我们都乐于看到这一幕{\r}\NWell, much as we'd all enjoy seeing something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我的镇没人会动用私刑{\r}\Nain't nobody gonna cheat the hangman in my town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很好，治安官，我们要出去了{\r}\NFair enough, marshal. Here we come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}外头情况有点紧张{\r}\NThey're a little tense out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别轻举妄动，让我来谈判{\r}\NSo don't make any quick movements, and let me do the talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}过来{\r}\NCome ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你没有武器？ - 没有{\r}\NYou unarmed? Yes, indeed we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}塔图治安官，容我跟你和你手下…{\r}\NMarshal Tatum, may I address you and your deputies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有所有道崔镇民…{\r}\Nand apparently the entire town of Daughtrey,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}解释刚才的事件{\r}\Nas to the incident that just occurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}继续{\r}\N- Go on. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我叫做金史华兹医生{\r}\NMy name is Dr. King Schultz.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.12,0:22:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}跟你一样，治安官 我也是执法人员{\r}\NLike yourself, marshal, I'm a servant of the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}死在污泥里的那个男人{\r}\NThe man lying dead in the dirt, who the good people of Daughtrey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.64,0:22:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}道崔镇的好乡民选出的警长 自称比尔夏普的那个人{\r}\Nsaw fit to elect as their sheriff, who went by the name of Bill Sharp,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}其实是名为威拉佩克的通缉要犯{\r}\Nis actually a wanted outlaw by the name of Willard Peck,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他的人头值200元{\r}\Nwith a price on his head of $200.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}无论生死都是200元{\r}\NNow that's $200, dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鬼扯蛋{\r}\NThe hell, you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我明白这也许是不堪的消息{\r}\NI'm aware this is probably disconcerting news.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我愿意打赌…{\r}\NBut I'm willing to wager this man was elected sheriff
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他在约两年前选上警长？{\r}\Nsometime in the past two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.52,0:22:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 对 - 我知道是因为三年前…{\r}\NYeah. I know this because three years ago, he was rustling cattle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他偷了德州寇瑞根畜牧公司的牛{\r}\Nfrom the B.C. Corrigan Cattle Company of Lubbock, Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是通缉令{\r}\NNow, this is a warrant
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}由德州奥斯汀巡回审判法官{\r}\Nmade out by Circuit Court Judge Henry Allen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}亨利艾伦罗德米克签署{\r}\NLaudermilk of Austin, Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你大可发电报问他{\r}\NYou're encouraged to wire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他会确认我的身分{\r}\NHe'll back up who I am and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}以及你们已故警长的身分{\r}\Nwho your dear departed sheriff was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}换句话说，治安官{\r}\NIn other words, marshal,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.72,0:23:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你欠我200元{\r}\Nyou owe me $200.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要死啦{\r}\NI'll be damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}毕氏的任务完成后{\r}\NAfter this Brittle business is behind us,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你就是自由民了{\r}\Nyou'll be a free man,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.60,0:24:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有马，口袋里有75元{\r}\Nwith a horse, $75 in your back pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}之后你有什么计划？{\r}\NWhat's your plan after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.76,0:24:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}找到我妻子{\r}\NFind my wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}买下她的自由之身{\r}\Nand buy her freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥{\r}\NDjango,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.00,0:24:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没想到你是已婚男人{\r}\N I had no idea you were a married man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.08,0:24:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}多数奴隶相信婚姻吗？{\r}\NDo most slaves believe in marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.47,0:24:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我和我妻子相信{\r}\NOh, me and my wife do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}卡洛肯大佬不相信 所以我们才逃走{\r}\NOld Man Carrucan didn't. That's why we... we run off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.80,0:24:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥{\r}\NDjango.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.84,0:24:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥，决哥{\r}\NDjango, Django-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.72,0:24:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你很有种，决哥{\r}\NYou got sand, Django.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.12,0:24:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这小子很有种{\r}\NBoy's got sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.80,0:24:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我用不着有种的黑鬼{\r}\NI got no use for a nigger with sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.48,0:25:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在他脸上烙了逃跑的“R”字{\r}\NI want you to burn a runaway "r" right here on his cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.32,0:25:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑女人也是{\r}\NAnd the girl, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.28,0:25:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把他们带到格林维尔拍卖会{\r}\NAnd I want you to take 'em to the Greenville auction
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.76,0:25:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}卖掉他们{\r}\Nand sell 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.08,0:25:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两个都是{\r}\NBoth of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.04,0:25:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}分开卖{\r}\NSeparately.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.44,0:25:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这个…{\r}\NAnd this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.08,0:25:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}便宜卖{\r}\Nyou will sell him cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.96,0:25:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在格林维尔…{\r}\NIn Greenville...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}应该有某种纪录处{\r}\Nthere should be some sort of a records office.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.16,0:25:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你已知道她被卖的时间{\r}\NYou know when she was sold...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.88,0:25:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她的卖家{\r}\Nyou know where she came from,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.96,0:25:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有她的名字{\r}\Nand you know her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.64,0:25:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她叫什么名字？{\r}\NWhat is her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.72,0:25:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布希达{\r}\NBroomhilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.56,0:25:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么？{\r}\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.76,0:25:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布希达{\r}\N- Broom-hilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.04,0:26:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布希达？{\r}\NBroomhilda?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.16,0:26:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她的主人是德国人？{\r}\N- Were her owners German?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.00,0:26:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你怎么知道？{\r}\N- Yeah, how you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.56,0:26:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她不是在卡洛肯庄园出生 她由德国女主人冯夏夫养大{\r}\NShe wasn't born on the Carrucan plantation. She was raised by a German mistress, the Von Shafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.44,0:26:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她也会说一点德语{\r}\NShe speak a little German, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.60,0:26:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你妻子？{\r}\NYour wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.80,0:26:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她小时候… 她的女主人教她用德语沟通{\r}\NWhen she was little, her mistress taught her so she'd have somebody to speak German with.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.52,0:26:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让我搞清楚{\r}\NWell, let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.24,0:26:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的奴隶妻子会说德语 她的名字叫布希达冯夏夫{\r}\NYour slave wife speaks German and her name is Broomhilda Von Shaft?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.96,0:26:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对{\r}\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.36,0:26:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大家叫我希达{\r}\NThey call me Hildi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.20,0:26:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（田纳西州）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.40,0:26:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（家中黑奴制服）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.72,0:26:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们进入这些庄园时{\r}\NWhen we gain access to these plantations,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.16,0:26:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们要假装演戏{\r}\Nwe'll be putting on an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.68,0:27:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要饰演一个角色{\r}\NYou'll be playing a character.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.32,0:27:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不好看？{\r}\NNo?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.44,0:27:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在演戏过程中，你绝不能穿帮{\r}\NDuring the act, you can never break character.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.28,0:27:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}了解吗？{\r}\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.40,0:27:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好，不能穿帮{\r}\NYeah. Don't break character.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.28,0:27:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的角色是侍从{\r}\NAnd your character is that of The Valet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.92,0:27:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么意思？{\r}\NWhat that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.36,0:27:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是仆人的好听说法{\r}\NThat's a fancy word for servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.96,0:27:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}侍从？{\r}\NValet?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.48,0:27:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥，现在你能选你角色的服装{\r}\NAnd now, Django, you may choose your character's costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.28,0:27:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要让我挑选自己的衣服？{\r}\NYouse gonna let me pick out my own clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.68,0:27:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那还用说{\r}\NBut of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.24,0:28:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这一区禁止黑鬼骑马{\r}\NIt's against the law for niggers to ride horses in this territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.64,0:28:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他是我的侍从，我的侍从不走路{\r}\NThis is my valet. My valet does not walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.24,0:28:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我说黑鬼骑马…{\r}\N- I said niggers on horses...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.44,0:28:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他叫做决哥，他是自由民 他想骑什么都行{\r}\N- His name is Django. He's a free man. He can ride what he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.20,0:28:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在我的地盘不行 在我的黑鬼面前不行{\r}\NNot on my property. Not around my niggers, he can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.40,0:28:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}亲爱的先生{\r}\NMy good sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.84,0:28:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或许初次见面搞砸了{\r}\Nperhaps we got off on the wrong boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.40,0:28:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}容我再来一次{\r}\NAllow me to unring this bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.12,0:28:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我叫做金史华兹医生 这是我的侍从决哥{\r}\NMy name is Dr. King Schultz. This is my valet, Django.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.84,0:29:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这些是我们的马，东尼和费兹{\r}\NAnd these are our horses, Tony and Fritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.96,0:29:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}班尼特先生？{\r}\NMr. Bennett?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.48,0:29:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我耳闻你是绅士和商人{\r}\NI've been led to believe that you are a gentleman and a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.28,0:29:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因此我们从德州到田纳西州{\r}\NAnd it is for these attributes we've ridden from Texas to Tennessee
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.12,0:29:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}来跟你谈判{\r}\Nto parley with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.00,0:29:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想买你的一个黑人女孩{\r}\NI wish to purchase one of your nigger gals.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.60,0:29:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你和你的侍从从德州到田纳西州{\r}\NYou and your Jimmie rode from Texas to Tennessee
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.00,0:29:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}来买我的一个黑人女孩？{\r}\Nto buy one of my nigger gals?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.96,0:29:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有事先约好？{\r}\NNo appointment, no nothin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.92,0:29:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}恐怕如此{\r}\NOh, I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.00,0:29:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要是我说我不喜欢你{\r}\NWell, what if I was to say I don't like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.52,0:29:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或你的臭屁黑鬼{\r}\NOr your fancy-pants nigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.28,0:29:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有我啥都不卖{\r}\NAnd I wouldn't sell you a tinker's damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.96,0:29:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你会怎么说？{\r}\NNow what you got to say about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.92,0:29:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}班尼特先生{\r}\NMr. Bennett.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.04,0:29:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果你是商人，我耳闻你是{\r}\NIf you are the businessman I've been led to believe you to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.72,0:29:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我有五千个理由让你改变心意{\r}\NI have 5,000 things I might say that could change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.84,0:30:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}进来吧，喝点凉的{\r}\NWell, come on inside and get yourself somethin' cool to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.48,0:30:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或许我们在谈生意时{\r}\NOh, maybe while we discuss business,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.44,0:30:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你能吩咐你的美丽黑人{\r}\Nyou could provide one of your loveliest black creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.64,0:30:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}带决哥参观你的宏伟领地{\r}\Nto escort Django here around your magnificent grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.52,0:30:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没问题{\r}\NOh, well, absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.88,0:30:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 贝蒂娜 - 是，大老爹{\r}\N Betina. Yes sir, Big Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.44,0:30:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你说你的侍从叫啥？{\r}\NWhat's your Jimmie's name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.40,0:30:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 决哥 - 决哥{\r}\N- Django. - Django.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.04,0:30:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}贝蒂娜，带决哥…{\r}\NBetina, sugar, could you take Django there
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.56,0:30:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到处逛逛，介绍珍奇美景{\r}\Nand take him around the grounds here and show him all the pretty stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.88,0:30:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}遵命，大老爹{\r}\NAs you please, Big Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.25,0:30:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}班尼特先生，我得提醒你，决哥是自由民{\r}\NOh, Mr. Bennett, I must remind you, Django is a free man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.36,0:30:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不能把他当奴隶看待{\r}\NHe cannot be treated like a slave. He... within the bounds of good taste,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.44,0:30:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}合乎礼仪的作法是 必须向对待我一样对待他{\r}\Nhe must be treated as an extension of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.64,0:30:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}了解，史华兹{\r}\N- Understood, Schultz.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.80,0:30:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 贝蒂娜甜心 - 是{\r}\NBetina, sugar? - Yes'm?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.60,0:30:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥不是奴隶 决哥是自由民，了解？{\r}\NDjango isn't a slave. Django is a free man, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.60,0:31:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对待他不能像是对待这里的黑人{\r}\NYou can't treat him like any of the other niggers around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.12,0:31:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他跟这里的黑人都不一样，懂吗？{\r}\N'cause he ain't like any of the other niggers around here. You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.16,0:31:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要我把他当白人？{\r}\NYou want I should treat him like white folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不对{\r}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.96,0:31:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不是这个意思{\r}\NThat's not what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.48,0:31:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那我不知道你要怎样，大老爹{\r}\NThen I don't know what you want, Big Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.32,0:31:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我明白了{\r}\NYes, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.52,0:31:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}镇上那个穷白人玻璃工叫啥名字？{\r}\NWhat's the name of that peckerwood boy from town that works with the glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.76,0:31:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他妈在制材场做事{\r}\NHis mama work over at the lumberyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.96,0:31:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你是说杰瑞 - 就是他，杰瑞{\r}\N- Oh, you mean Jerry. - That's the boy's name. Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.84,0:31:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 甜心，你知道杰瑞吧？ - 是，大老爹{\r}\NYou know Jerry, don't you, sugar? - Yes'm, Big Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.04,0:31:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没错，就像对杰瑞一样对待他{\r}\N- Well, that's it, then.You just treat him like you would Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.52,0:31:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}刚才那间房子是“大房子”{\r}\NThat house we just left from is The Big House.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.60,0:31:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大老爹这样叫，因为很大{\r}\NBig Daddy call it that 'cause it's big.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.60,0:31:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那里是食品室{\r}\NThat there is the pantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.04,0:31:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大老爹把死动物储藏在那里{\r}\NThat's where Big Daddy hang all his dead meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.64,0:31:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可怜的松鼠{\r}\NPo' little squirrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.36,0:32:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你替你的主人做什么？{\r}\NWhat you do for your massa?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.00,0:32:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没听到他说我不是奴隶？{\r}\NDidn't you hear him tell you I ain't no slave?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.16,0:32:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你真是自由之身？ - 对，我是自由之身{\r}\N- So you really free? - Yes, I's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.64,0:32:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你是说你自己想穿成这样？{\r}\NYou mean you wanna dress like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.80,0:32:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 贝蒂娜，我要问你一件事 - 你要干嘛？{\r}\N- Betina, I need to ask you somethin'. - What you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.72,0:32:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我在找三个白人，三兄弟，监工{\r}\NI'm lookin' for three white men. Three brothers. Overseers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.96,0:32:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 姓毕，听过吗？ - 毕？{\r}\NTheir name is Brittle. You know 'em? - Brittle?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.76,0:32:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，姓毕 毕约翰、毕艾利斯、毕罗杰{\r}\N- Yes, Brittle. John Brittle, Ellis Brittle, Roger Brittle,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.20,0:32:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有时也叫小拉杰{\r}\Nsometime called Lil Raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.96,0:32:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我没听过{\r}\NI don't know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.08,0:32:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们可能用化名{\r}\NThey could be usin' a different name.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.20,0:32:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他们应该是去年来这里的 - 你是说夏佛兄弟？{\r}\NThey woulda come to the plantation this past year. - You mean the Shaffers?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.24,0:32:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或许，三兄弟？{\r}\N- Maybe. Three brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.44,0:32:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们在这里？{\r}\NThey here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.52,0:32:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}能指出其中一个吗？{\r}\NCould you point one of 'em out to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.72,0:32:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一个在那里的草地{\r}\NWell, one's over in that field.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.24,0:33:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}卡洛肯大佬会不高兴{\r}\NOld Man Carrucan ain't gonna appreciate this, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.72,0:33:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她在主人家工作 让她破相就不妙了{\r}\NShe work in the house, John. You could mess her skin up, and you gonna mess her up
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.72,0:33:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她会变得一无可取{\r}\Nand she ain't gonna be worth... she ain't gonna be worth a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.04,0:33:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的圣经上说{\r}\NNow, your Bible say...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.24,0:33:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}听着，我说过是我逼她的{\r}\NLook, I told you that I was one that made her do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.04,0:33:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 准备好了？ - 她不想跟我逃跑{\r}\NYou ready? She didn't wanna run off with me. If anybody should be gettin' whupped now,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.80,0:33:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要打就打我，约翰{\r}\Nit should be me. It should be me, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.80,0:33:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我在这里很久了，你早就认识我{\r}\NNow, I been here long enough, you know me, you know me a long time, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.28,0:33:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}卡洛肯主人会不高兴，她是家奴{\r}\NYou know Massa Carrucan ain't gonna appreciate this. She's a... she's a house slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.14,0:33:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She a house slave, she can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.24,0:34:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我求你，拜托 你不是就想要我哀求你{\r}\NOn my knees. I'm asking you this, please. Ain't this what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.58,0:34:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}约翰，拜托{\r}\NI'm keeping it funny for you. Now, John, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.40,0:34:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我跪下了，约翰{\r}\NL's on my knees, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.12,0:34:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我喜欢你乞求的贱样{\r}\NI like the way you beg, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.72,0:34:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你想找的是那个人吗？{\r}\NIs that who you was lookin' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.84,0:34:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对{\r}\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.20,0:34:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}另外两个呢？{\r}\NWhere the other two at?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.76,0:34:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在马棚旁，在教训小裘蒂弄破蛋{\r}\NThey by the stable, punishin' Little Jody for breakin' eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.80,0:34:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们鞭打小裘蒂？{\r}\NThey whippin' Little Jody?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.96,0:34:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}指出方向给我看{\r}\NPoint me in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.32,0:34:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}走到那棵树，再继续走那边{\r}\NYou go to that tree and keep goin' that-a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.28,0:34:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}去找来跟我的白人同伴{\r}\NGo get that white man I came here with.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.72,0:34:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 快点 - 不要，拜托{\r}\N- Come on, now. - No, no, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.48,0:34:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点，丫头{\r}\N- Come on, girlie. - Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.00,0:34:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点  把你绑好了{\r}\NCome on. Get you set up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.80,0:34:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“上帝说，汝之恐惧”{\r}\N"And the Lord said, 'The fear of ye..."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.34,0:35:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“与汝之敬畏 将如同世间的所有禽兽”{\r}\N"...and the dread of ye shall be on every beast of the earth."'
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.16,0:35:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把手伸好{\r}\NCome here now, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.68,0:35:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再不把手伸好你就完了{\r}\NYou'd better give me that arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.84,0:35:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好，她准备好了{\r}\NOK, she's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.80,0:35:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看你以后还敢不敢弄破蛋{\r}\NAnd after this, we'll see if you break eggs again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.16,0:35:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}毕约翰{\r}\NJohn Brittle!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.76,0:36:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}记得我吗？{\r}\NYou remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.56,0:36:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我喜欢你死的样子{\r}\NI like the way you die, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.32,0:36:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}死王八蛋！{\r}\NGoddamn son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.04,0:36:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}哀求我啊{\r}\NKeep it funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.00,0:37:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大家想看精彩的？{\r}\NY'all wanna see somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.04,0:37:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不要{\r}\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.84,0:37:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们是谁？{\r}\NWho were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.08,0:37:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那是大约翰{\r}\NThat's Big John,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.52,0:37:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那是小拉杰{\r}\Nand that's Lil Raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.24,0:37:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}艾利斯呢？{\r}\NWhere's Ellis?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.72,0:37:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在原野上窜逃的那个人{\r}\NHe's the one hightailin' it across that field right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.96,0:37:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 确定是他？ - 对{\r}\N- You sure that's him? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.68,0:37:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 肯定？ - 不明白{\r}\N- Positive? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.20,0:37:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你不明白自己肯不肯定？ - 我不明白“肯定”是什么意思{\r}\N- You don't know if you're positive? - I don't know what "positive" mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.28,0:37:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 就是确定 - 对{\r}\N- It means you're sure. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.84,0:37:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 什么“对”？ - 对，我确定那是毕艾利斯{\r}\N- "Yes," what? - Yes, I'm sure that's Ellis Brittle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.00,0:38:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我肯定他死了{\r}\NI'm positive he dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.72,0:38:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥！{\r}\NDjango!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.68,0:38:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大家冷静，我们不想伤害任何人{\r}\NEverybody calm down. We mean no one else any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.64,0:38:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们两个小丑是谁？{\r}\NWho are you two jokers?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.48,0:38:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是金史华兹医生 美国刑法制度的…{\r}\NI am Dr. King Schultz, a legal representative
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.52,0:38:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}合法代表{\r}\Nof the criminal justice system of the United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.36,0:38:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我左边这位是决哥自由民 他是我的副手{\r}\NThe man to my left is Django Freeman. He's my deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.88,0:38:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我口袋里有通缉令{\r}\NIn my pocket is a warrant,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.20,0:38:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}由德州奥斯汀巡回审判法官 亨利艾伦罗德米克签署{\r}\Nsigned by Circuit Court Judge Henry Allen Laudermilk of Austin, Texas,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.76,0:38:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}下令逮捕和俘虏，无论生死{\r}\Nfor the arrest and capture, dead or alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.52,0:38:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}毕约翰、毕罗杰、毕艾利斯{\r}\Nof John Brittle, Roger Brittle and Ellis Brittle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.44,0:38:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们化名为夏佛兄弟{\r}\NThey were goin' by the name Shaffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.00,0:39:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你以为他们姓夏佛 但这群屠夫的本姓是毕{\r}\NYou know them by the name of Shaffer, but the butchers' real name was Brittle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.52,0:39:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们是通缉犯，因谋杀罪依法通缉{\r}\NThese are wanted men. The law wants 'em for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.96,0:39:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在我重申{\r}\NNow, I reiterate,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.56,0:39:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}通缉令上明令“无论生死”{\r}\Nthe warrant states dead or alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.40,0:39:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所以我和自由民先生当场处决他们{\r}\Nso when Mr. Freeman and myself executed these men on sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.88,0:39:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们是在法律范围内行动{\r}\Nwe were operating within our legal boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.16,0:39:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我明白你满腔怒火{\r}\NI realize passions are high,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.96,0:39:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我得警告你{\r}\Nbut I must warn you,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.72,0:39:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}采取致命武力…{\r}\Nthe penalty for taking deadly force
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.12,0:39:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}违抗法庭官员行使职责的刑罚是{\r}\Nagainst an officer of the court in the performance of his duty
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.53,0:39:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你会被吊死{\r}\Nis you'll be hung by the neck until you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.56,0:39:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在请容我拿出通缉令给你检查{\r}\NNow, may I please remove the warrant from my pocket so you may examine it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.40,0:39:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}给我{\r}\NGimme.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.16,0:40:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}满意了？{\r}\NSatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.00,0:40:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请还我{\r}\NMay I have that back, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.72,0:40:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}滚出我的地盘{\r}\N- Get off my land.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.44,0:40:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}立马走人{\r}\N- Posthaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.52,0:40:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}尽快带走尸体，快走人{\r}\NLoad up the bodies as quickly as you can and let's get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.80,0:40:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，是那两个王八蛋{\r}\NYeah, that's them sons-a-bitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.44,0:41:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点{\r}\NCome on, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.76,0:41:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有胆别走，黑鬼{\r}\NWe're coming for you, nigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.56,0:41:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}除非他们先开枪{\r}\NNow, unless they start shootin' first,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.44,0:41:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不准有人开枪{\r}\Nnobody shoot 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.16,0:41:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那样对这些小丑太客气了{\r}\NThat's way too simple for these jokers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.04,0:42:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们要把哈黑鬼的白人鞭死{\r}\NWe're gonna whup that nigger-lover to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.12,0:42:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我还要亲自把那个黑鬼阉了{\r}\NAnd I'm gonna personally strip and clip that garboon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.88,0:42:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可恶{\r}\NDamn.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.36,0:42:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}戴这玩意我啥都看不到{\r}\NI can't see fuckin' shit outta this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.68,0:42:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}准备好了没？{\r}\NWe ready or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.80,0:42:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等等，我弄一下眼洞{\r}\NHold on, I'm fuckin' with my eyeholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.87,0:42:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}靠，愈弄愈糟{\r}\NOh... Oh, shit. I just made it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.72,0:42:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 这烂玩意谁做的？ - 维拉的妻子{\r}\NWho made this goddamn shit? - Willard's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.96,0:42:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不然你们自己做面罩啊{\r}\N - Well, make your own goddamn masks!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.08,0:42:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别误会，大家都感谢珍妮的服务{\r}\NLook, nobody's sayin' they don't appreciate what Jenny did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.96,0:42:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要是我只是在袋子上钻洞 我能钻得更好{\r}\NWell, if all I had to do was cut a hole in a bag, I coulda cut it better than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.56,0:42:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}罗伯，你呢？看得到吗？{\r}\NWhat about you, Robert? Can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.40,0:42:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有点遮到{\r}\NNot too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.88,0:42:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不转头看你会比较清楚{\r}\NI mean, if I don't move my head I can see you pretty good, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.40,0:42:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但骑马时面罩会乱动 好像瞎子骑马{\r}\NBut when I start ridin', the bag's movin' all over, and I'm ridin' blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.08,0:42:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}靠{\r}\N- Shit. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.56,0:42:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我也愈弄愈糟{\r}\NI just made mine worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.11,0:42:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.48,0:42:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谁还有备用的？{\r}\NAnybody bring any extra bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.20,0:43:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没啦，谁会有备用的{\r}\NNo, nobody brought an extra bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.32,0:43:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我只是问问 - 骑马时一定要戴吗？{\r}\NI'm just askin'. Do we have to wear 'em when we ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.08,0:43:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}靠，骑马时不戴…{\r}\NOh, well, shitfire! If you don't wear 'em as you ride up,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.24,0:43:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 就白搭了 - 戴这玩意我看不到{\r}\Nthat just defeats the purpose! Well, I can't see in this fuckin' thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.80,0:43:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我无法呼吸，戴这玩意我不能骑马{\r}\NI can't breathe in this fuckin' thing and I can't ride in this fuckin' thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.72,0:43:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}去你们的，我要回家了{\r}\NWell, fuck all y'all! I'm goin' home!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.16,0:43:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看我老婆辛苦整天{\r}\NNow, I watched my wife work all day
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.44,0:43:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}替你们这群忘恩负义的王八蛋 一口气钻了30个袋子{\r}\Ngettin' 30 bags together for you ungrateful sons-a-bitches,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.48,0:43:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我却只听到批评、批评、批评！{\r}\Nand all I can hear is criticize, criticize, criticize!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.40,0:43:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}以后别叫我或我老婆帮忙{\r}\NFrom now on, don't ask me or mine for nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.60,0:43:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}听着 别忘了我们在这里的目的{\r}\NNow, look, let's not forget why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.00,0:43:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那边的山区有个黑鬼杀手 我们要给他教训{\r}\NWe got a killer nigger over that hill there! And we gotta make a lesson out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.76,0:43:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我搞糊涂了 到底要不要戴面罩？{\r}\NOK, I'm confused. Are the bags on or off?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.76,0:43:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大家都觉得面罩是个好主意{\r}\NI think we all think the bag was a nice idea. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.84,0:43:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但没针对谁，面罩能做得更好{\r}\NBut, not pointin' any fingers, they coulda been done better.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.92,0:43:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}干脆这次不戴面罩{\r}\NSo how 'bout no bags this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.72,0:44:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}下次把面罩做对再披挂上阵{\r}\Nbut next time we do the bags right and then we go full regalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.64,0:44:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 好主意 - 我投你一票{\r}\N- I like that idea a lot. - You get my vote, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.84,0:44:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等一下{\r}\NWait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.48,0:44:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我没同意{\r}\NI didn't say no bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.48,0:44:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但大家都看不到{\r}\NBut nobody can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.92,0:44:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 所以咧？ - 看到会比较好{\r}\NSo? So it'd be nice to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.20,0:44:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}妈的，这是袭击，大家都看不到{\r}\NGoddamn it! This is a raid! I can't see, you can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.12,0:44:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那又怎样？最重要的是马看得到 这是袭击{\r}\NSo what? All that matters is can the fuckin' horse see! That's a raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.33,0:44:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}王八蛋！{\r}\NSons of bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.72,0:44:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我啥都看不到{\r}\NI can't see shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.88,0:44:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他在那里 把黑鬼从马车下撵出来{\r}\NThere he is! Get that nigger out from under that wagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.04,0:44:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}也把他麻吉从马车下撵出来{\r}\NAnd get that nigger-lover outta the wagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.44,0:44:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 黑鬼不在下面，大老爹 - 什么？{\r}\NThat nigger ain't down here, Big Daddy! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.04,0:44:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他们在耍我们 - 那他们在哪里？{\r}\N- They tricked us! Well, where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.24,0:44:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再会了{\r}\NAuf Wiedersehen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.08,0:44:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}正中目标{\r}\NBull's-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.04,0:44:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看他们落跑了{\r}\NLook at 'em run.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.24,0:45:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}孬种常会那样{\r}\NYeah, cowards tend to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.82,0:45:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可恶{\r}\NGoddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.88,0:45:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可恶{\r}\NGoddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.76,0:45:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想试试吗？{\r}\NWould you care to?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.40,0:45:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}啥都看不见{\r}\NCan't see shit outta this!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.84,0:45:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他要逃走了 - 我会干掉他{\r}\N- He's getting away. - I got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.00,0:45:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大老爹要逃走了{\r}\NBig Daddy's getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.68,0:45:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我会干掉他{\r}\NI got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.08,0:45:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}干掉他了{\r}\NGot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.00,0:46:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你是天生好手{\r}\NThe kid's a natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.84,0:46:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你怎知布希达前主子是德国人？{\r}\NHow you know Broomhilda's first masters was German?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.76,0:46:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布希达是德国名字{\r}\NBroomhilda is a German name.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.76,0:46:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这表示命名者必然是德国人{\r}\NIf they named her, it stands to reason they'd be German.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.04,0:46:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的庄园有很多女生叫布希达吗？{\r}\NLots of gals where you're from named Broomhilda?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.08,0:46:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布希达是一个角色名称{\r}\NBroomhilda is the name of a character
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.16,0:46:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在最著名的德国传奇中{\r}\Nin the most popular of all the German legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.24,0:46:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有故事在讲布希达？{\r}\NThere's a story about Broomhilda?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.28,0:46:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，没错{\r}\NOh, yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.08,0:46:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你熟悉吗？{\r}\N- Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.40,0:46:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}每个德国人都知道那个故事{\r}\N- Oh, every German knows that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.92,0:46:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要我告诉你吗？{\r}\NWould you like me to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.00,0:47:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布希达曾是公主{\r}\NWell, Broomhilda was a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.76,0:47:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她是万神之王沃坦的女儿{\r}\NShe was a daughter of Wotan, god of all gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.84,0:47:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}总之她爸非常气她{\r}\NAnyway, her father is really mad at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.24,0:47:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她做了什么？{\r}\NWhat she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.40,0:47:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不太记得了{\r}\NI can't exactly remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.12,0:47:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她就是不服从他{\r}\NShe disobeys him in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.96,0:47:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}于是他把她送到山顶{\r}\NSo he puts her on top of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.52,0:47:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布希达在山上？{\r}\NBroomhilda's on a mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.08,0:47:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是德国传奇，一定会有山{\r}\NIt's a German legend, there's always going to be a mountain in there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.28,0:47:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他安排一只喷火龙守着山{\r}\NAnd he puts a fire-breathing dragon there to guard the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.04,0:47:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他用地狱之火把她围住{\r}\NAnd he surrounds her in a circle of hellfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.72,0:47:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布希达会一直受困在那里{\r}\NAnd there, Broomhilda shall remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.28,0:47:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}除非有英雄鼓足勇气拯救她{\r}\NUnless a hero arises brave enough to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.56,0:47:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有英雄挺身而出吗？{\r}\NDoes a fella arise?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.52,0:47:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有，决哥，事实上有{\r}\NYes, Django, as a matter of fact, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.72,0:47:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那个人叫做齐格弗里{\r}\NA fella named Siegfried.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.20,0:48:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}齐格弗里有拯救她吗？{\r}\NDoes Siegfried save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.80,0:48:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那是一场壮举{\r}\NQuite spectacularly so.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.16,0:48:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他攀登那座山，因为他不害怕{\r}\NHe scales the mountain, because he's not afraid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.96,0:48:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他屠杀那只龙，因为他不怕他{\r}\NHe slays the dragon, because he's not afraid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.40,0:48:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他穿过地狱之火{\r}\NAnd he walks through hellfire...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.16,0:48:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因为布希达值得{\r}\Nbecause Broomhilda's worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.60,0:48:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我懂他的感觉{\r}\NI know how he feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.72,0:48:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我开始能体会了{\r}\NI think I'm just starting to realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.12,0:48:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}听着，决哥{\r}\NNow, look, Django...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.32,0:48:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你肯定会拯救你深爱的女人{\r}\NI don't doubt that one day you'll save your lady love...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.40,0:48:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我不能昧着良心让你去格林维尔{\r}\Nbut I can't let you go to Greenville in a good conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.24,0:48:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}密西西比州的奴隶拍卖镇 不是你该去的地方{\r}\NA slave auction town in Mississippi isn't the place for you to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.76,0:49:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}无论自不自由，都太危险了{\r}\NFree or not, it's just too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.64,0:49:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我问你一个问题{\r}\NBut let me ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.12,0:49:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你喜欢赏金猎人的工作吗？{\r}\NHow do you like the bounty hunting business?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.20,0:49:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}杀白人还有钱领？{\r}\NKill white folks and they pay you for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.32,0:49:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}干嘛不喜欢{\r}\NWhat's not to like?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.80,0:49:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我得承认，我们是好搭档{\r}\NNow, I have to admit, we make a good team.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.12,0:49:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我以为你不爽我杀了大约翰和小拉杰{\r}\NI thought you was mad at me for killin' Big John and Lil Raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.64,0:49:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那件事你是有点热心过度 但正常来说是好事{\r}\NYeah, on that occasion you were a tad overzealous, but normally, that's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.44,0:49:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这个冬天想要合伙吗？{\r}\NHow'd you like to partner up for the winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.88,0:49:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“合伙”是指什么？{\r}\NWhat you mean "partner up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.00,0:49:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你跟我合作直到冬天结束{\r}\NYou work with me through the winter till the snow melts...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.20,0:49:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我给你三分之一的赏金{\r}\NI give you a third of my bounties.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.44,0:49:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这个冬天挣点钱，等到雪溶化{\r}\NSo we make some money this winter, and when the snow melts,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.88,0:49:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我亲自带你去格林维尔{\r}\NI'll take you to Greenville myself
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.84,0:49:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们会查出你妻子被送去哪里{\r}\Nand we'll find where they sent your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.04,0:50:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你何必关心我会怎样？{\r}\NWhy you care what happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.60,0:50:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}何必关心我能不能找到老婆？{\r}\NWhy you care if I find my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.84,0:50:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}坦白说{\r}\NFrankly...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.56,0:50:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我从没赋予任何人自由{\r}\NI've never given anybody their freedom before.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.44,0:50:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在既然有，多少感觉对你有责任{\r}\NAnd now that I have, I feel vaguely responsible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.48,0:50:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}加上德国人遇到实际的齐格弗里 这可就大条了{\r}\NPlus, when a German meets a real life Siegfried, that's kind of a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.64,0:50:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}身为德国人，我有义务帮你…{\r}\NAs a German, I'm obliged to help you on your quest
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.08,0:50:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}冒险营救你心爱的布希达{\r}\Nto rescue your beloved Broomhilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.68,0:52:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你熟能生巧了{\r}\NYou got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.54,0:52:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“我要射杀白人领钱”  先生怎么了？{\r}\NWhat happened to Mr. "I Wanna Shoot White Folks For Money"?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.80,0:52:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他儿子在旁{\r}\N- His son's with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.28,0:52:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很好，他死时有家人陪{\r}\N- Well, good. He'll have a loved one with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.40,0:52:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或许还能说遗言{\r}\NMaybe even share a last word.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.64,0:53:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}比多数人死得痛快{\r}\NThat's better than most of them get.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.92,0:53:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他算是赚到了{\r}\NDamn sight better than he deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.52,0:53:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把枪放下{\r}\NPut down the rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.76,0:53:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别担心，我不是气你{\r}\NDon't worry, I'm not mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.36,0:53:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拿出史密提毕考的传单{\r}\NLet's take out Smitty Bacall's handbill.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.48,0:53:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大声念出{\r}\NRead it aloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.92,0:53:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}当作今天学到一课{\r}\NConsider that today's lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.16,0:53:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“通缉，无论生死”{\r}\N"Wanted. Dead or alive."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.88,0:53:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“史密提毕考和史密提毕考一…”{\r}\NSmitty Bacall and the Smitty Bacall
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.00,0:53:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 一帮人 - “一帮人”{\r}\N- Gang. - "Gang."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.36,0:53:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“因谋杀和马车…”{\r}\N"For murder and stagecoach..."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.60,0:53:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“抢劫”{\r}\Nrobbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.08,0:53:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“70…” - Seven-zero-zero-zero.. - Seven thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.76,0:53:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.80,0:53:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“7000元悬赏史密提毕考”{\r}\N"$7,000 for Smitty Bacall."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.96,0:54:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“1500元悬赏他的…”{\r}\N$1,500 for each of his...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.40,0:54:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“一帮同…”{\r}\Ngang...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.52,0:54:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}同…？{\r}\N- Mem...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.80,0:54:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“同伙”{\r}\N- "Members."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.72,0:54:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“史密提毕考帮的已知同伙如…”{\r}\NKnown members of the Smitty Bacall Gang are as follas:"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.40,0:54:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 如下 - “如下”{\r}\N- Follows. - "Follows."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.64,0:54:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“丹尼麦可斯、杰拉德纳许…”{\r}\N"Dandy Michaels, Gerald Nash and..."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.44,0:54:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}疯子克雷格库。恩{\r}\NCrazy Craig Koons.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.16,0:54:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史密提毕考就是这种恶棍{\r}\NThat is who Smitty Bacall is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.00,0:54:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果史密提毕考22岁时立志开农场 这张传单就绝不会存在{\r}\NIf Smitty Bacall wanted to start a farm at 22, they would never have printed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.48,0:54:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但是史密提毕考想要抢劫马车{\r}\NBut Smitty Bacall wanted to rob stagecoaches
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.00,0:54:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他为达目的滥杀无辜{\r}\Nand he didn't mind killing people to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.24,0:54:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你想要效法我替天行道救你爱妻？{\r}\NDo you want to save your wife by doing what I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.64,0:54:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这就是我的使命{\r}\NThis is what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.36,0:54:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我杀人和卖尸体领钱{\r}\NI kill people and sell their corpses for cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.84,0:54:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这具尸体值7000元{\r}\NThis corpse is worth $7,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.56,0:54:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别再龟毛了，射杀他{\r}\NNow quit your pussyfooting and shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.12,0:55:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}爸？{\r}\NPa?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.56,0:55:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}爸！{\r}\NPa!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.48,0:55:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拿去{\r}\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.84,0:55:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}留着这张史密提毕考的传单{\r}\NYou need to keep this Smitty Bacall handbill.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.32,0:55:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}为什么？{\r}\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.52,0:55:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是幸运符 切记随身携带首次赏金的传单{\r}\N- It's good luck. You always keep the handbill of your first bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.36,0:56:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很准{\r}\NThat's accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.20,0:57:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}医生、决哥，你们好啊{\r}\NDoctor, Django, how the hell are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.32,0:57:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们干掉谁了？{\r}\NWho the hell-a you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.60,0:57:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}威尔森罗尔帮{\r}\NThe Wilson-Lowe Gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.00,0:57:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}威尔森罗尔帮是谁？{\r}\NWho the hell is the Wilson-Lowe Gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.60,0:57:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}坏蛋威尔森与更狠的巴比罗 还有他们的三个手下{\r}\NBad Chuck Wilson and meaner Bobby Lowe and three of their acolytes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.25,0:57:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别管他们，他们又不会跑掉{\r}\NWell, just leave 'em out here, they ain't going nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.12,0:57:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}外头冰天雪地，进来喝点咖啡{\r}\NWhy don't you come in then out of the snowy snow and get yourselves some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.52,0:57:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昨天我们庆生，有些蛋糕{\r}\NWe had a birthday yesterday. Got some cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.64,0:57:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很好{\r}\NPretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.56,0:58:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（经过收获丰厚的寒冬之后）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.28,0:58:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（决哥和史华兹医生下山）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.24,0:58:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（前往…）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.44,0:58:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（密西西比州）{\r}\NMove along!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.54,0:58:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.20,0:58:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}继续走，向拍卖区行进{\r}\NKeep movin'. Get on up on that auction block.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.96,0:58:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别因泥地放慢脚步，继续走{\r}\NDon't let that mud slow you down. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.92,0:58:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}继续走{\r}\NKeep goin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.64,0:58:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“布希达冯夏夫”{\r}\N"Broomhilda Von Shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.52,0:58:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“27岁”{\r}\NAge 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.60,0:59:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“右脸颊烙了“R”字”{\r}\N'R' on right cheek."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.52,0:59:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（凯文康迪）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.76,0:59:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“凯文康迪”{\r}\NCalvin Candie.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.28,0:59:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他拥有密西西比第四大的棉花庄园 糖果园{\r}\NHe owns the fourth biggest cotton plantation in Mississippi: Candyland.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.88,0:59:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}糖果园？{\r}\NCandyland?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.40,0:59:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 原来你听过 - 所有奴隶都听过糖果园{\r}\NOh, so you've heard of it. Ain't no slave ain't heard of Candyland.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.00,0:59:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}显然你妻子在那里{\r}\NWell, apparently, that's where your wife is...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.56,0:59:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那个恶霸名绅拥有她{\r}\Nand that's the repellant gentleman
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.47,0:59:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}希望她在主人家工作，不是田野{\r}\Nwho owns her. Let's just hope she works in the house, not in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.28,0:59:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她才不是田野的黑奴{\r}\NOh, no, she ain't no field nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.56,0:59:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她很漂亮{\r}\NShe... she pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.24,0:59:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她也很会说话{\r}\NAnd she talk good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.48,0:59:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但自从她被痛鞭{\r}\NBut when they tore her back up and then they...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.92,0:59:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}脸上还烙了逃跑的“R '’字{\r}\Nburned that runaway "r" on her cheek...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.08,0:59:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她就毁了{\r}\Nthey goddamned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.00,0:59:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她不是田野的黑奴 但她也不再够格在主人家做事{\r}\NShe ain't no field nigger but she ain't good enough for the house no more either.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.84,0:59:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 她会被逼去当慰安妇 - 慰安妇？懂了{\r}\NThey gonna try to make her a comfort girl. What's a comfort...?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.92,0:59:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是自由之身说休想{\r}\NNot while I got freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.00,0:59:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我有枪就休想{\r}\NNot while I got my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.28,1:00:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那我们要出价买她吗？{\r}\NSo do we offer to buy her?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.32,1:00:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}姑且…{\r}\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.28,1:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}说…{\r}\Nsay...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.88,1:00:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有个人想要买只马{\r}\Na man wants to buy a horse.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.24,1:00:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}需要买只马{\r}\NNeeds to buy a horse.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.40,1:00:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他去农人的农场，敲农人的门{\r}\NHe walks up to the farmer's farm, and he knocks on the farmer's door
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.40,1:00:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要求买农人的马 知道农人会怎么说？{\r}\Nand asks the farmer to buy his horse. And do you know what the farmer says?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.32,1:00:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}农人拒绝{\r}\NThe farmer says no.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.00,1:00:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}去他妈的农人，我用偷的{\r}\NWell, I say fuck that farmer, and I'm stealin' that horse.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.04,1:00:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有道理，但你说变成偷马贼{\r}\NFair enough. But now you're a horse thief,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.52,1:00:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}偷马贼会被吊死{\r}\Nand they hang horse thieves.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.44,1:00:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}更不用说马会送回原主人 因为马仍是他的财产{\r}\NNot to mention the horse goes back to its original owner because the horse is still his property.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.60,1:00:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们需要她，也需要销售收据{\r}\NWe need her and we need a bill of sale.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.28,1:00:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我们不买她的话要怎么获得她？{\r}\NWell, if we ain't gonna try to buy her, then how we gonna get her?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.08,1:00:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我能提供行动备案吗？{\r}\NMay I offer an alternative plan of action?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.88,1:00:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}说吧{\r}\NGo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.35,1:01:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}买家去农人的农场，敲农人的门{\r}\NSo... the man walks up to the farmer's farm, he knocks on the farmer's door...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.44,1:01:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不是要求买马，而是农场{\r}\Nand asks not to buy the horse, but the farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.96,1:01:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}开出高得离谱的报价{\r}\NAnd makes an offer so ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.28,1:01:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}农人不得不答应{\r}\Nthe farmer is forced to say yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.76,1:01:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我们要出价买糖果园？ - 不，那太大了{\r}\N- We gonna offer to buy Candyland? - No, it's far too big.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.84,1:01:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但显然这个农人不只在意农场{\r}\NBut apparently this farmer ain't all about the farm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.16,1:01:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你多了解曼丁果格斗？{\r}\NHow much do you know about Mandingo fighting?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.68,1:01:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么？{\r}\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.88,1:01:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你能煞有其事地扮成…{\r}\NCan you convincingly masquerade as someone
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.40,1:01:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}曼丁果格斗的专家吗？{\r}\Nwho is an expert on Mandingo fighting?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.68,1:01:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}为什么？{\r}\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.08,1:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因为我的角色是 来到格林维尔的德国大买家{\r}\NBecause my character is that of a big money buyer from Dusseldorf,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.76,1:01:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想要洒钱打入曼丁果格斗赛{\r}\Nhere in Greenville to buy my way into the Mandingo fight game.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.32,1:01:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的角色是我雇来的曼丁果专家{\r}\NAnd your character is a Mandingo expert I hired to help me do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.32,1:01:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}即江湖人称的“独眼查理”{\r}\NThey call that "One-Eyed Charley."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.48,1:01:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你好 - 晚安{\r}\NBonjour.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.24,1:01:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的黑人小妞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.04,1:01:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们来见凯文康迪先生{\r}\NWe're here to see Mr. Calvin Candie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.04,1:01:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请进{\r}\NEntraz.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.92,1:01:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.60,1:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要我扮演黑人奴隶商？{\r}\NYou want me to play a black slaver?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.44,1:02:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这种人最贱了{\r}\NAin't nothin' lower than a black slaver.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.28,1:02:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑人奴隶商比黑奴总管更贱{\r}\NA black slaver is lower than the head house nigger...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.28,1:02:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}伙伴，就是贱到不行{\r}\Nand, buddy, that's pretty fuckin' low.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.72,1:02:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那就演贱一点{\r}\NThen play him that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.64,1:02:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}演好你的黑人奴隶商{\r}\NGive me your black slaver.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.44,1:02:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along came the 219 Toot! Toot! Peanut butter!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.36,1:02:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史医生{\r}\NDr. Schultz!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.24,1:02:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 喜重逢啊 - 摩盖先生{\r}\N- Good to see you again! - Mr. Moguy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.12,1:02:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}感谢协助安排这次约见的机会{\r}\NThank you for your assistance in creating the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.48,1:02:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别客气，这是我的本分{\r}\N- for this appointment. - Nonsense, it's my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.44,1:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这位就是久闯大名的独眼查理吧{\r}\NSo this is the One-Eyed Charley I've heard so much about.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.52,1:02:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，这位是决哥自由民{\r}\NYes, this is Django Freeman.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.04,1:02:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥，这位是凯文康迪的律师 李奥奈摩盖{\r}\NDjango, this is Mr. Candie's lawyer, Leonide Moguy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.00,1:02:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}叫我李奥就好{\r}\NJust call me Leo.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.92,1:02:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}凯文在凯撒大帝室，请跟我来{\r}\NCalvin's in the Julius Caesar room. You all wanna follow me?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.44,1:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你跟康迪先生认识多久了？{\r}\NHow long have you been associated with Mr. Candie?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.20,1:03:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我和凯文的父亲11岁时 一起上寄宿学校{\r}\NOh, Calvin's father and I were about 11 when we went to boarding school together.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.56,1:03:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}凯文的祖父付钱让我读完法学院{\r}\NCalvin's father's father put me through law school.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.60,1:03:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}几乎能说我被栽培成凯文的律师{\r}\NOne could almost say I was raised to be Calvin's lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.92,1:03:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}几乎跟黑奴一样{\r}\NOne could almost say youse a nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.48,1:03:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你说什么？{\r}\NWhat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.16,1:03:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我说……  - 没事，他在耍冷{\r}\N- I said... - Nothing, he's just being cheeky.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.32,1:03:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}见康迪先生前还要注意他哪些事？{\r}\NAnything else about Mr. Candie that I should know before I meet him?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.92,1:03:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有，他是亲法国人士{\r}\NYes, he is a bit of a Francophile.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.32,1:03:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上流人士不都这样？{\r}\NWhat civilized people aren't?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.00,1:03:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他喜欢称作康迪男士胜于康迪先生{\r}\NAnd he prefers Monsieur Candie to Mr. Candie.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.52,1:03:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（随他高兴）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.88,1:03:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他不会说法语 别跟他说法语，他会很糗{\r}\NHe doesn't speak French. Don't speak French to him, it'll embarrass him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.92,1:03:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}回到上面！转身！{\r}\NGet back on top, now! Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.48,1:03:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很好{\r}\NThere you go. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.40,1:03:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你为什么想要进入曼丁果业？{\r}\NWhy do you want to get in the Mandingo business?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.48,1:03:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不必由你的副手正式介绍？{\r}\NYou don't intend to allow your second to make the proper introductions?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.36,1:03:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}少废话，回答问题{\r}\NQuit stalling, now. Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.12,1:04:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}糟糕的真相？{\r}\NThe awful truth? I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.32,1:04:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我太闷了，这似乎很好玩{\r}\NThis seems like a good bit of fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.24,1:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}过来坐{\r}\NWell, come on over.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.40,1:04:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在正在格斗，很好玩{\r}\NWe got us a fight goin' on that's a good bit of fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.84,1:04:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}陪我去吧台吧{\r}\NWon't you accompany me to the bar?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.88,1:04:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}室内要脱帽，白人，连我都知道{\r}\NYou don't wear a hat in the house, white man. Even I know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.04,1:04:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 史医生 - 万分高兴{\r}\N- Dr. Schultz. - What a rare pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.04,1:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}继续斗，黑鬼{\r}\NKeep fighting, niggers.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.64,1:04:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}容我补充，也很荣幸{\r}\N- And I might add, an honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.60,1:04:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}幸会，请坐，荣幸之至{\r}\N- Honor to meet you. Please have a seat, the pleasure's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.56,1:04:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看自由民决哥想喝什么{\r}\NGet free man Django here whatever he wants.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.20,1:04:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要甜茶和波本酒{\r}\NAnd I'll have sweet tea and bourbon.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.12,1:05:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}利用你的重量，很好{\r}\NUse your weight, boy, use your weight! There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.56,1:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他高大又强壮多了{\r}\NHe's much bigger and stronger!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.92,1:05:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拼了啦{\r}\NCome on, now!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.64,1:05:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他没照我的话做，乱七八糟{\r}\NHe's not doing what I told him, for God's sakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.52,1:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}赞啦，鲁吉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.20,1:05:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拼了，这是一场殊死战{\r}\NCome on, now, boy! It's a fight to the death!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.14,1:05:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你到底要不要干掉他？{\r}\NYou either hit him or are you ain't?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.32,1:05:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大佛莱，加油{\r}\NBig Fred, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.32,1:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把他转过来，快点{\r}\NTurn him around! Now...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.60,1:05:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}加把劲{\r}\NUse your strength, boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.96,1:05:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点，加把劲{\r}\NCome on, now! Use your strength!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.08,1:06:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很好{\r}\NThere you go!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.40,1:06:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很好{\r}\NThere you go!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.84,1:06:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你瞧{\r}\N Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.72,1:06:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看吧，我就说出手要更重{\r}\NSee, I told you to put some more power in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.96,1:06:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}照我的话做{\r}\NDo what I told you, boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.12,1:06:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很好{\r}\NThere you go!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.96,1:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不要！{\r}\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.32,1:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}照我的话做{\r}\N- Do what I told ya!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.48,1:06:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}挖出他的眼珠，挖出他的眼珠{\r}\NBlind him black, boy! Blind him black!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.64,1:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不，鲁吉{\r}\NOh, no, Luigi.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.48,1:06:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好耶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.04,1:06:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}杀掉他{\r}\NFinish him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.52,1:06:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点，杀掉他{\r}\NGo on, boy, finish him!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.72,1:06:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}名不虚传大佛莱，绝对值回票价{\r}\NThat's why they call him Big Fred.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.51,1:07:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再会，鲁吉{\r}\N- Worth every penny.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.24,1:07:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快起来，休息一下{\r}\N- Well, arrivederci, Luigi. Come on up, now, boy. Get yourself a rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.64,1:07:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}表现很好，好极了{\r}\NYou did a fine job. A real fine job.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.04,1:07:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}摩西黛{\r}\NMercedes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.88,1:07:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}龙舌兰{\r}\NTequila.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.08,1:07:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}怎么称呼？{\r}\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.84,1:07:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥{\r}\NDjango.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.72,1:07:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}怎么拼？{\r}\NCan you spell it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.52,1:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}D一J一A一N一G一O{\r}\ND-J-A-N-G-O.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.08,1:07:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}处决的决{\r}\NThe D is silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.16,1:08:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我知道{\r}\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.20,1:08:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}安贝托，走吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.40,1:08:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}摩盖先生，照顾我的新宠{\r}\NMr. Moguy, want you to take care of my new boy here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.00,1:08:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}给他有软床的房间 找个黑妞替他吹喇叭{\r}\NYou find him a room with a soft bed, then you bring him up a pony to lick his pole.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.48,1:08:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但明早准备好来糖果园，明白没？{\r}\NBut you be ready to travel to Candyland tomorrow morning, now, ya hear?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.72,1:08:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 遵命，康迪男士 - 走之前{\r}\NYessir, Monsieur Candie. Before you go,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.28,1:08:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}罗斯柯，给佛莱一瓶啤酒{\r}\NRoscoe, get Fred here a tall beer.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.48,1:08:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好好享用，你应得的{\r}\NYou enjoy that, boy. You've earned it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.72,1:08:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}遵命{\r}\NYessir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.12,1:08:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你叫什么名字？{\r}\N- What's your name, boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.88,1:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他的名字是决哥自由民{\r}\N- His name is Django Freeman.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.72,1:08:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你哪里找到他的？{\r}\NWhere'd you dig him up?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.56,1:08:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥和我是有缘千里来相会{\r}\NA fortuitous turn of events brought Django and myself together.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.44,1:08:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我对你略有耳闻{\r}\NI've heard tell about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.16,1:09:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}听说你宣称那些曼丁果选手烂透了{\r}\NI heard you been telling everybody them Mandingos ain't no damn good.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.28,1:09:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}市场上的曼丁果黑奴都不值得买{\r}\NAin't nothin' nobody is sellin' is worth buyin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.51,1:09:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我很好奇  你凭什么成为曼丁果专家？{\r}\NI'm curious... what makes you such a Mandingo expert?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.68,1:09:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我好奇是什么让你这么好奇{\r}\NI'm curious what makes you so curious.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.44,1:09:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你说什么？ - 冷静，布奇{\r}\N- What did you say, boy? - Calm down, Butch.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.52,1:09:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有恶意{\r}\NNo offense given...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.52,1:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}也不以为意{\r}\Nnone taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.96,1:09:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪男士{\r}\NMonsieur Candie...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.72,1:09:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我建议你有问题直接问我{\r}\NI'd appreciate if you could direct your line of inquiry toward me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.68,1:09:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}首先{\r}\NOne...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.64,1:09:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你没有饮料，想喝点什么吗？{\r}\Nyou do not have anything to drink. Can I get you a tasty refreshment?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.08,1:09:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 好，我要啤酒 - 太好了{\r}\N- Yes! I'll have a beer. - Wunderbar.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.92,1:09:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}罗斯柯，给大胡子男一瓶啤酒{\r}\NRoscoe, a beer for the man with the beard,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.20,1:09:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要玻里尼亚潜水采珠人 兰姆酒不能少{\r}\Nand I will have a Polynesian Pearl Diver. Do not spare the rum.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.24,1:09:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}医生{\r}\NDoc...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.40,1:09:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是经验丰富的奴隶商 你是新手{\r}\NI am a seasoned slaver. You are, well, you are a neophyte.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.88,1:09:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我只是想确定这个牛仔…{\r}\NI'm simply tryin' to ascertain if this cowboy here
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.16,1:09:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有没有占你便宜{\r}\N is takin' advantage of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.40,1:09:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}恕我直言，康迪男士{\r}\NWith all due respect, Monsieur Candie...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.16,1:10:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我找你不是想要你的指点{\r}\NI didn't seek you out for your advice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.48,1:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}而是想要以市场最高价 买个格斗黑人{\r}\NI sought you out to purchase a fighting nigger at above top-dollar market price.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.04,1:10:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你同意见我时，我以为…{\r}\NNow I was under the impression, when you granted me an audience,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.44,1:10:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这次是来谈生意的{\r}\Nit would be to discuss business.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.32,1:10:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们还不谈生意{\r}\NWell, we weren't talkin' business yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.84,1:10:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们谈我的好奇心{\r}\NWe were discussin' my curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.44,1:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.64,1:10:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}罗斯柯，可可，去外头玩{\r}\NRoscoe, Coco, go outside and play.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.36,1:10:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}夏芭，你留下{\r}\NSheba... you stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.84,1:10:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我知道你不是指我{\r}\NI know you didn't mean me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.40,1:10:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 干杯 - 德国人{\r}\N- Prost! - German.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.68,1:10:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}据摩盖所说{\r}\NNow, according to Moguy,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.56,1:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果我跟你做生意{\r}\Nif I do business with you,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.68,1:10:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就是跟你们俩做生意{\r}\NI'm doing business with both y'all.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.88,1:10:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他挑人，你付钱，是吗？{\r}\NHe does the eyeballin', you the billfold? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.48,1:10:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}直截了当，但差不多{\r}\NWell, you don't make it sound too flattering, but more or less, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.76,1:10:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所以…{\r}\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.36,1:10:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好小子 摩盖说你查看了我的黑人选手{\r}\NBright Boy... Moguy tells me you looked over my African flesh
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.12,1:11:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}全看不上眼，是吗？{\r}\Nand you was none too impressed?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.56,1:11:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有高档货{\r}\NNot for top dollar.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.04,1:11:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那我们没什么好谈了{\r}\NWell, then, we got nothin' more to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.24,1:11:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你想要向我买普通选手{\r}\NYou see, you wanna buy a beat-ass nigger from me,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.56,1:11:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我就只有那些货色{\r}\Nthose are the beat-ass niggers I wanna sell so...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.20,1:11:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他不想买你想卖的黑人{\r}\NHe don't wanna buy the niggers you wanna sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.96,1:11:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他想买你不想卖的黑人{\r}\NHe wants the nigger you don't wanna sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.40,1:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不卖我不想卖的黑人{\r}\NWell, I don't sell the niggers I don't wanna sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.96,1:11:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不会卖最好的{\r}\NWell, you won't sell your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.80,1:11:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}连第二好的也不卖{\r}\NYou won't even sell your second best.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.32,1:11:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那第三好的呢？你也不想卖{\r}\NBut your third best...? You don't want to sell him either.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.00,1:11:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但如果我开出高到离谱的价格 你就不得不考虑{\r}\NBut if I made you an offer so ridiculous you'd be forced to consider it...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.20,1:11:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谁晓得会不会有谱？{\r}\Nwho knows what could happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.36,1:11:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你怎么定义“离谱”？{\r}\NAnd what do you consider ridiculous?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.44,1:11:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天赋异秉的奇人 独一无二的黑人？{\r}\NFor a truly talented specimen, the right nigger?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.48,1:11:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥，你说多少？{\r}\NHow much would you say, Django?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.72,1:12:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}12000元{\r}\NTwelve thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.24,1:12:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两位，你们原本令我好奇{\r}\NWell, gentlemen, you had my curiosity,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.20,1:12:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在你们引起我的注意了{\r}\Nbut now you have my attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.92,1:12:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}威利，威利{\r}\NWillie. Willie.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.32,1:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}停车，停车{\r}\NHold up! Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.60,1:12:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 早安，各位 - 史医生啊{\r}\N- Good morning, gentlemen. - Good Dr. Schultz.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.56,1:12:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 美好的早晨，对吧？ - 好到没得比{\r}\N- Beautiful morning, isn't it? - You couldn't have picked a better one.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.36,1:12:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请上车，跟我们去兜风{\r}\NPlease, won't you take a ride with us here in the Victoria.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.48,1:12:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}感谢赏光{\r}\NOh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.96,1:12:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的马能绑在后面{\r}\NYou can tie your horse up back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.36,1:12:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥{\r}\NDjango.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.44,1:13:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我跟友人、同僚的不同之处{\r}\NWhere I part company from many of my phrenologist colleagues
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.36,1:13:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在于我相信有一种等级能超越智慧{\r}\Nis I believe there is a level
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.64,1:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}超越天资、超越忠诚{\r}\Nabove bright, above talented,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.60,1:13:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑人梦寐以求的典范{\r}\Nabove loyal that a nigger can aspire to.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.96,1:13:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}比如出现万中选一的黑人{\r}\NSay, one nigger that just pops up in 10,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.72,1:13:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}非比寻常的黑人{\r}\NThe exceptional nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.28,1:13:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好日子吧，好小子？{\r}\NBright day Bright Boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.44,1:13:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}太阳出来了{\r}\NSun is up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.76,1:13:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}照耀我们所有人{\r}\NShining on all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.40,1:13:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请坐，医生{\r}\N- Have a seat, doc. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.56,1:13:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}荣幸至极{\r}\NQuite an honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.00,1:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 与有荣焉 - 谢谢{\r}\N- The honor is all ours. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.20,1:13:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我相信随着时间{\r}\NBut I do believe that, given time,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.52,1:13:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}像这位好小子一样的不寻常黑人{\r}\Nexceptional niggers like Bright Boy here...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.12,1:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}即使仍不常见{\r}\Nbecome if not frequent...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.28,1:13:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但会变得更常见{\r}\Nmore frequent.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.72,1:13:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对吧？{\r}\NBright Boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.96,1:13:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你就是万中选一{\r}\Nyou are that one in 10,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.64,1:13:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这个局是要跟得上，不是赶不上{\r}\NThe name of the game is keep up, not catch up, nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.60,1:14:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 敢碰枪，你就死定了 - 各位，冷静{\r}\N- Touch your guns, you die. - Everybody, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.72,1:14:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}综观全局，没有恶意{\r}\NNow I saw the whole thing. No harm done.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.00,1:14:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 没搞错？这黑人… - 我说没有恶意{\r}\NAre you kidding me? - This nigger just... - I said no harm done!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.32,1:14:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}手不准碰枪{\r}\NNow take your hand off your pistol!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.96,1:14:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布奇，你也是{\r}\NButch, that means you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.96,1:14:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所有人别再敌视我的客人{\r}\NEverybody stop antagonizing my guest.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.28,1:14:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡特，上马{\r}\NHoot! Get back up on your horse.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.32,1:14:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他弄断我的锁骨{\r}\NHe broke my collarbone!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.00,1:14:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}搞屁，谁快来扶胡特上马{\r}\NFor God's sake, somebody please help Hoot here back up on his goddamn horse.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.60,1:14:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 遵命，老板 - 你是走运的黑人{\r}\N- Yessir, boss. - Oh, now you are one lucky nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.40,1:14:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你最好听你老板的话，白人小子{\r}\NYou better listen to your boss, white boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.56,1:14:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要跟你在月光下漫步{\r}\NOh, I'm gonna go walking in the moonlight with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.20,1:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你想牵我的手？{\r}\NYou wanna hold my hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.60,1:15:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}威利，送我们回家{\r}\NWillie, take us home.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.36,1:15:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好了，开始行进{\r}\NStart moving!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.96,1:15:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}叫奴隶快走{\r}\NHead 'em out!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.64,1:16:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你眼睛有问题吗？{\r}\NYou got a problem with your eyeball, boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.96,1:16:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 没有 - 要我把你眼睛踹正吗？{\r}\NNo, sir. You want a boot heel in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.52,1:16:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不用{\r}\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.72,1:16:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那就少瞪着我{\r}\NThen you keep your goddamn eyeballs off me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.72,1:16:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再给我臭脸，就给你好看{\r}\NYou flash that bad look at me again, I'll give you a reason not to like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.40,1:16:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快走，黑人{\r}\NNow move, nigger!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.80,1:16:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们这些黑人会见识到老子的厉害{\r}\NYou niggers are gonna understand something about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.16,1:16:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我比这些白人更可怕{\r}\NI'm worse than any of these white men here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.52,1:16:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别慢吞吞了，别死盯着我了{\r}\NYou get the molasses out your ass, you keep your goddamn eyeballs off me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.32,1:16:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他活力旺盛呢{\r}\NHe is a rambunctious sort, ain't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.20,1:16:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}确实{\r}\NIndeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.96,1:16:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}能暂停一下吗？ 我想跟我的伙伴说句话{\r}\NMay we stop for a moment so I may put a word in my man's ear?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.60,1:16:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我见到糖果园的选手想必会很在意{\r}\NYou know, I'm expecting to fall in love once I see the specimens at Candyland,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.48,1:16:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所以在那之前{\r}\Nso before that moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.08,1:16:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我希望跟我的密友有个… 机密的策略会议{\r}\Nit would be good if I could have  a confidential strategy meeting with my confidant.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.12,1:16:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}能透露你在干嘛吗？{\r}\NYou mind telling me what the hell you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.08,1:16:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我已确认布希达在糖果园{\r}\NI confirmed that Broomhilda's at Candyland.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.00,1:17:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 确定是她？ - 他没说她的名字{\r}\N- You're sure it's her? - He didn't call her by name,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.92,1:17:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但有个年轻女孩 背后有鞭打疤痕，会说德语{\r}\Nbut she's a young lady, whip marks on her back and speaks German.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.64,1:17:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}虽然在现况下这种假设并不乐见{\r}\NNow, while it's not wise to assume,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.48,1:17:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但八九不离十{\r}\Nin this instance, I think it's pretty safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.12,1:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}重点是{\r}\NPoint being,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.76,1:17:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不要满脑子想着报复{\r}\Ndon't get so carried away with your retribution.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.92,1:17:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你忘记我们来这里的目的{\r}\NYou lose sight of why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.84,1:17:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你以为我忘记了？ - 没错，别再杠上康迪{\r}\N- You think I lost sight of that? - Yes, I do. Stop antagonizing Candie.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.48,1:17:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你会让我们穿帮，会害死我们{\r}\NYou're going to blow this whole charade, or more than likely get us both killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.76,1:17:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我可不想死在 美国密西西比州的契卡索郡{\r}\NAnd I, for one, don't intend to die in Chickasaw County, Mississippi, USA.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.64,1:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不会杠上他，我会智取他{\r}\NI'm not antagonizing him. I'm intriguing him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.20,1:17:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你对这群可怜的奴隶鬼叫耶{\r}\NYou're yelling abuse at these poor slaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.16,1:17:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想起有个人…{\r}\NI recall the man
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.60,1:17:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}命令我在别人儿子面前杀人{\r}\Nwho had me kill another man in front of his son
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.88,1:17:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他连眼睛都没眨一下{\r}\Nand he didn't bat a eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.16,1:17:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你记得吧？{\r}\NYou remember that?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.32,1:17:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我当然记得了{\r}\NYeah, of course I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.96,1:17:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你教过我，这是我的世界{\r}\NWhat you said was that this is my world...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.24,1:18:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想要翻身难免得弄脏手{\r}\Nand in my world you gotta get dirty.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.44,1:18:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所以我照做，把手弄脏{\r}\NSo that's what I'm doing. I'm gettin' dirty.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.04,1:18:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你有点曲解我的意思{\r}\NWell, you're paraphrasing a tad, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.68,1:18:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但主旨相差不远{\r}\Nthat was the general gist.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.56,1:18:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}糖果园见{\r}\NSee you at Candyland.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.72,1:18:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好，黑人们，继续走{\r}\NAll right, niggers, back at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.56,1:18:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你也是，月光{\r}\NThat means you too, Moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.76,1:19:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不会吧{\r}\NI'll be. D'Artagnan!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.16,1:19:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}达太安！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.04,1:19:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}小子，干嘛蠢到逃跑？{\r}\NNow, boy, why do a fool thing like run off?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.36,1:19:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不能再格斗了，康迪男士{\r}\NI can't fight no more, Monsieur Candie.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.88,1:19:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你当然能{\r}\NYes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.20,1:19:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你也许赢不了，但你还能打{\r}\NYou might not be able to win, but your ass can fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.88,1:19:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史东赛佛先生，叫这些死狗闭嘴 我无法专心思考{\r}\NMr. Stonesipher, would you please shut these goddamn dogs up? - I cannot hear myself think!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.96,1:19:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}安静，玛夏，小声{\r}\N- Quiet down, Marsha! Marsha, hush up! Marsha!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.68,1:19:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}玛夏，小声{\r}\NHush up! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.68,1:19:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把这些狗牵走{\r}\NGet these goddamn dogs away from this nigger!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.28,1:20:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 小子，别趴在树上了 - 是的{\r}\NCome on now, boy... get on out that tree. Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.12,1:20:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他逃跑多久？{\r}\NHow long was he loose?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.36,1:20:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一晚，白天{\r}\NA night. Day.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.80,1:20:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再半晚{\r}\NHalf the other night.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.40,1:20:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他逃离多远？{\r}\NHow far he get off the property?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.40,1:20:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}约20英里，以他瘸腿来说挺远的{\r}\N'Bout 20 miles off the prop. Pretty far considering that limp he got.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.04,1:20:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}摩盖先生 周五达太安预计跟谁对打？{\r}\NMr. Moguy, who was D'Artagnan supposed to fight on Friday?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.56,1:20:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这群新人的其中一个{\r}\NOne-a this new lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.24,1:20:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看他现在的样子 连瞎眼的印地安人都不会赌他赢{\r}\NWell, way he looks now, a blind Indian wouldn't bet a bead on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.56,1:20:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拜托，康迪男士，我不能再打了{\r}\NPlease, Monsieur Candie, I ain't got it in me no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.56,1:20:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}够了…不准乞求{\r}\N- Now, now, now, now, now. - I can't... Now, no beggin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.16,1:20:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别激起我的软心肠{\r}\NNo playin' on my soft heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.16,1:21:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你闯祸了 - 是{\r}\N- You in trouble now, son. - Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.48,1:21:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我付了500元买你{\r}\NI done paid $500 for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.44,1:21:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我付500元时{\r}\NWhen I pay $500,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.84,1:21:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我预期一名黑奴挂掉前打五场{\r}\Nthen I expect to get five fights out of a nigger'fore he roll over and play dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.24,1:21:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是的{\r}\N- Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.44,1:21:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要了解我是生意人{\r}\NYou got to understand that I'm runnin' a business here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.88,1:21:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你打过三场 - 但我赢了每一场{\r}\N- You fought three fights. - But I won every one.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.84,1:21:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，没错{\r}\NYes, you did. Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.48,1:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但上一场，你差点输了{\r}\NBut that last one, you muddled the line between winnin' and losin'. Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.28,1:21:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}事实依然不变{\r}\NStill, the fact remains:
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.60,1:21:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我付500元，我就要五场比赛{\r}\NI pay $500, I want five goddamn fights!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.60,1:21:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不然我的500元怎么办？{\r}\NSo what about my $500?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.80,1:21:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的500元怎么办？{\r}\NWhat about my $500?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.16,1:21:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要补偿我吗？{\r}\NYou gonna reimburse me?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.92,1:21:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你懂不懂“补偿”的意思啊？{\r}\NYou even know what "reimburse" means?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.64,1:22:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我会补偿你{\r}\NI'll reimburse you!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.16,1:22:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你愿意？{\r}\NYou Will?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.60,1:22:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对{\r}\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.80,1:22:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你愿意付500元{\r}\NYou'll pay $500
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.72,1:22:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}买这个几乎独眼 连扫把都拿不动的废人？{\r}\Nfor practically a one-eyed old Joe ain't fit to push a broom?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.44,1:22:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不，他不愿意{\r}\NNo, he won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.60,1:22:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他只是受够你玩弄他{\r}\NHe just tired of you toyin' with him is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.80,1:22:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}事实上，我也是{\r}\NMatter of fact, so am I.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.04,1:22:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我们不会付一分钱买那个黑仔{\r}\NBut we ain't payin' a penny for that pickaninny.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.48,1:22:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他没用了 对吧，医生？{\r}\NAin't got no use for him. Ain't that right, doc?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.16,1:22:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你听到他了{\r}\NYou heard him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.56,1:22:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你得原谅史东赛佛先生 吓得目瞪口呆{\r}\NYou're gonna have to excuse Mr. Stonesipher's slack-jawed gaze.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.32,1:22:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他这辈子没见过你这种黑人{\r}\NHe ain't never seen a nigger like you ever in his life.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.76,1:23:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史东赛佛先生，对吧？{\r}\NAin't that right, Mr. Stonesipher?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.16,1:23:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没错{\r}\NThat right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.48,1:23:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就此而言{\r}\NFor that matter...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.28,1:23:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我也没看过{\r}\Nnor have I.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.88,1:23:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在{\r}\NNow...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.04,1:23:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}既然你们不付钱买这个黑仔{\r}\Nseein' as you won't pay a penny for this pickaninny here...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.80,1:23:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不介意他随我处置吧？{\r}\Nyou won't mind me handlin' this nigger any way I see fit?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.20,1:23:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他是你的黑人{\r}\NHe's your nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.52,1:23:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史东赛佛先生？{\r}\NMr. Stonesipher?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.56,1:23:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让玛夏和她的狗同伴 送达太安下黑人地狱吧{\r}\NLet Marsha and her bitches send D'Artagnan to nigger heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.44,1:23:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}玛夏！{\r}\NMarsha!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.44,1:23:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}玛夏，咬他{\r}\NMarsha, hey, get him!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.12,1:23:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}咬他，咬他{\r}\NGet 'im, get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.02,1:23:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.56,1:24:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你老板的脸色发青 目睹这种媲美黑人格斗的血腥场面{\r}\NYour boss looks a little green around the gills for a blood sport like nigger fighting.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.32,1:24:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不，他只是不习惯看到 人被狗大卸八块{\r}\NNah, he just ain't used to seein' a man ripped apart by dogs is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.60,1:24:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你就习惯？{\r}\NYou are used to it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.24,1:24:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我比他习惯美国作风{\r}\NI'm just a little more used to Americans than he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.28,1:24:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪男士{\r}\NNow, Monsieur Candie...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.92,1:24:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}准备出发了吧{\r}\Nwhenever you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.96,1:24:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们走了5小时让你炫耀货色 该赶路了{\r}\NWe rode five hours so you could show off your stock. Let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.60,1:24:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}目前为止，如果他是示范 没啥了不起{\r}\N'Cause as of now, if he's an example, I ain't impressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.96,1:25:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}走吧{\r}\NFollow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.56,1:25:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（哈里斯费德公司）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.68,1:26:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（凯文康迪）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.92,1:27:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让他们在左边排好队{\r}\NLine 'em up to the left here now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.12,1:27:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}站直{\r}\NStand up straight, now!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.44,1:27:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上去那里{\r}\NGet up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.88,1:27:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上去那里，快点{\r}\NGet up there, boy. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.48,1:27:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}叫你们排队，快排队 排好，站直{\r}\NGive me a line! Give me a line! Get in line there! Straighten up!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.16,1:28:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你好，史提芬，老兄{\r}\NHello! Stephen, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.96,1:28:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你好啊，老兄个头{\r}\NYeah, yeah, yeah. Hello, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.96,1:28:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这个骑马的黑鬼是谁？{\r}\NWho this nigger up on that nag?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.80,1:28:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史提芬，你早餐吃钉子？ 怎么了？干嘛话中带刺？{\r}\NStephen, you have nails for breakfast? What's-a matter? Why you so ornery?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.96,1:28:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你很想我吧 - 是的{\r}\N- You miss me? - Oh, yessir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.16,1:28:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想死你了{\r}\NI miss you like a hog miss slop!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.76,1:28:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就像宝宝想念妈妈的咪咪{\r}\NLike a baby miss mammy's titty.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.76,1:28:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想你就像想念鞋里的石子{\r}\NI miss you like I misses a rock in my shoe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.16,1:28:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我问你，这个骑马的黑鬼是谁？{\r}\NWho this nigger on that nag?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.72,1:28:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}嗨，白人跟班{\r}\NHey, Snowball?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.68,1:28:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想要知道我或我马儿的名字 直接问我{\r}\NWanna know my name or the name of my horse, you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.36,1:28:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}骑马仔，你叫谁白人跟班？{\r}\NJust who the hell you callin' "Snowball," horse boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.44,1:28:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我会瞬间把你拖下马摔落泥地 快到你的头会打转{\r}\NI'll snatch your black ass off that nag there and in the mud so fast...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.24,1:29:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史提芬…{\r}\N- ...make your head spin. - Stephen, Stephen, Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.12,1:29:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别坏了兴致，决哥是自由民{\r}\NLet's keep it funny. Django here's a free man.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.52,1:29:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 这个黑人？ - 没错{\r}\N- This nigger here? - That nigger there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.92,1:29:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好歹让我介绍你们俩{\r}\NLet me at least introduce the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.40,1:29:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥，这是跟你一样拽的黑人 史提芬{\r}\NDjango, this is another cheeky black bugger like yourself, Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.48,1:29:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史提芬，这是决哥 你们俩应该互相讨厌{\r}\NStephen, this here's Django. You two oughta hate each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.88,1:29:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}凯文，这黑人算哪根葱 让你觉得有必要款待？{\r}\NCalvin, just who the hell is this nigger you feels the need to entertain?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.88,1:29:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥和他的灰衣朋友史医生 是顾客{\r}\NDjango and his friend in gray here, Dr. Schultz, are customers.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.16,1:29:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们是我们的客人{\r}\NAnd they are our guests, Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.84,1:29:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你这老不休该殷勤招待他们{\r}\NAnd you, you old decrepit bastard, oughta show them every hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.44,1:29:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 明白了没？ - 遵命，他的话我知道{\r}\N- You understand that? - Yessir. Him I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.64,1:29:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我不明白为何要忍受这黑人吐槽{\r}\NBut I don't know why I got to take lip off this nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.36,1:29:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不必懂原因，明白了没？{\r}\NYou don't have to know why. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.36,1:29:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 遵命，我知道了 - 很好{\r}\NYessir. I understand. Well, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.56,1:29:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们要过夜 去楼上准备好两间客房{\r}\NThey're spendin' the night. Go up in the guest bedrooms and get two ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.76,1:29:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他要住在主屋？{\r}\NHe gonna stay in The Big House?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.60,1:29:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史提芬，他是奴隶商，是特例{\r}\NStephen, he's a slaver. It's different.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.08,1:29:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 住在主屋？ - 你有意见吗？{\r}\N- In The Big House? - Well, you got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.76,1:29:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没，小的没意见{\r}\NOh, no. I ain't got no problem with it,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.16,1:29:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只是这脏黑人离开时{\r}\Nif you ain't got no problem with burnin' the bed, the sheets,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.32,1:30:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不心疼把床、被单、枕头都给烧了{\r}\Nthe pillowcases, everything else when this black-ass motherfucker's gone!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.24,1:30:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那是我的问题，我的东西随我烧{\r}\NThat is my problem! They are mine to burn!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.56,1:30:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你现在的问题是留下好印象{\r}\NNow your problem right now is makin' a good impression!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.96,1:30:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还不快解决问题，把客房准备好{\r}\NAnd I want you to start solvin' that problem right now and get them goddamn rooms ready!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.80,1:30:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}遵命，康迪男士{\r}\NYessir, Monsieur Candie.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.92,1:30:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快去{\r}\NGo on, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.60,1:30:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不敢相信你带个黑人来住主屋{\r}\NCan't believe you brought a nigger to stay in The Big House.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.92,1:30:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你爸会从坟里爬出来{\r}\NYour daddy rollin' over in his goddamned grave.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.20,1:30:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}瞧他说话  嘴巴愈来愈贱{\r}\NMan, the lip on him. He's gettin' worse and worse. Now...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.24,1:30:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的美丽姊姊呢？{\r}\NWhere is my beautiful sister?!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.12,1:30:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她来了{\r}\NThere she is!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.52,1:30:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史医生，这位迷人的南方美女 是我守寡的姊姊{\r}\NDr. Schultz, this attractive Southern belle is my widowed sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.68,1:30:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}亲爱的，看到你就精神百倍{\r}\NDarlin', you are a tonic for tired eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.72,1:30:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}容我介绍拉拉莉康迪费兹威利{\r}\NMay I present to you Lara Lee Candie-Fitzwilly.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.32,1:30:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}切斯特、罗德尼、小查理 全过去畜栏那里{\r}\NChester, Rodney, Chicken Charly. Y'all get your ass over by that pen.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.12,1:30:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 快点，查理，赶快 - 快走，快点{\r}\N- Come on, Charly. Come on, now! - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.56,1:30:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们知道地点，冲过去{\r}\NYou know where it is. Like you on a rope!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.32,1:31:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这里的黑人不准走路，只准跑步{\r}\NNiggers don't walk around here, niggers run!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.52,1:31:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪男士{\r}\NMonsieur Candie?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.08,1:31:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}关于你聊到的那个黑人女孩{\r}\NYeah. About that matter about the nigger girl you were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.00,1:31:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑人女孩？{\r}\NNigger gal?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.20,1:31:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，我记得你提到她会说德语{\r}\NYeah, I believe you mentioned she spoke German.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.92,1:31:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，希达，她怎样？{\r}\NYes! Hildi, what about her?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.16,1:31:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你想在挑货色之前 能送她到我房间吗？{\r}\NDo you think before the demonstration, you could send her around to my room?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.84,1:31:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你这色胚，有何不可{\r}\NYou little dickens, you. I don't see why not.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.52,1:31:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史提芬，带他们进房之后 去叫希达{\r}\NStephen, when you get through showin' them to their rooms, go fetch Hildi,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.52,1:31:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让她洗得香喷喷 送她到史医生的房间{\r}\Nget her cleaned up and smellin' real nice, and sent over to Dr. Schultz's room here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.24,1:31:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪男士，其实有件事我还没告诉你{\r}\NActually, Monsieur Candie, sir, there's-a somethin' I ain't told you 'bout yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.56,1:31:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 什么？ - 希达在地窖{\r}\N- What? - Hildi in the Hot Box.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.80,1:31:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她跑到那里干嘛？{\r}\NWhat's she doin' there?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.16,1:31:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不然你以为咧？她受到惩罚啊{\r}\NWhat you think she doin' there in the Hot Box? She bein' punished.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.48,1:31:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 她做了什么？ - 她又逃走了{\r}\N- What she do? - She run off again.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.16,1:31:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要命，史提芬 我不在时跑掉多少人？{\r}\NJesus Christ, Stephen, how many people ran away while I was gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.24,1:31:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 两个 - 她何时逃的？{\r}\N- Two. - When did she go?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.48,1:31:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昨晚，今早被带回来{\r}\NLast night. They brung her back this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.84,1:32:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史东赛佛的狗把她咬得多惨？{\r}\NHow bad did Stonesipher's dogs tear her up?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.92,1:32:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她运气好，狗都去追达太安了{\r}\NLucky for her, they was out chasin' D'Artagnan's ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.60,1:32:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}比尔和寇帝去找她 发现她就带她回来{\r}\NBill and Cody went lookin' for her, found her, brung her back.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.52,1:32:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在她伤痕累累{\r}\NNow, she a little beat-up.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.08,1:32:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但她从树林逃走是自找罪受{\r}\NBut she done that to her own damn self runnin' through them damn bushes and shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.52,1:32:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她在地窖里多久了？{\r}\NHow long she been in the box?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.20,1:32:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你以为多久？当然是整天{\r}\NHow long you think she been in there? All damn day.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.28,1:32:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那个小贱人要再关十天{\r}\NAnd the little bitch got ten more days to be in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.56,1:32:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 还是放她出来 - 放她出来？为什么？{\r}\N- Still, take her out. - Take her out? Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.36,1:32:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因为老子说的，没为什么{\r}\NBecause I said so, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.40,1:32:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史医生是我的客人 希达是我的黑奴{\r}\NDr. Schultz is my guest. Hildi is my nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.36,1:32:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}南方的好客就是要以客为尊{\r}\NSouthern hospitality dictates I make her available to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.72,1:32:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 可是康迪男士，她逃走耶 - 要命，史提芬{\r}\N- But, Monsieur Candie, she run off. - Jesus Christ, Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.96,1:32:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}养个会说德语的黑奴{\r}\NWhat is the point of havin' a nigger that speaks German
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.12,1:32:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}却不让她服侍德国客人有何意义？{\r}\Nif you can't wheel 'em out when you have a German guest?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.92,1:32:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我明白时机不当 但你还是要放她出来{\r}\NNow, I realize it is inconvenient, but still, you take her ass out.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.68,1:32:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}遵命{\r}\NYessir.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.32,1:32:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拉拉莉，你和柯拉负责…{\r}\NLara Lee! Will you and Cora be responsible
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.08,1:32:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}帮希达洗净和打扮，献给史医生{\r}\Nfor gettin' Hildi cleaned up and presentable for Dr. Schultz here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.88,1:32:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 当然{\r}\NOf course, darlin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.07,1:33:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两位 亲爱的 我道歉 我旅途奔波累到不行{\r}\NNow, gentlemen, I do apologize, but I am weary from our travels beyond words.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.16,1:33:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我该眯一下了{\r}\NIt is time for me to rest my tired eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.72,1:33:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们都听到老板的话了 把她拖出来{\r}\NY'all done heard the man! Get her ass up outta there!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.00,1:33:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}柯拉，过来{\r}\NCora! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.46,1:33:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}去帮她洗干净  再把她送到那个医生…{\r}\NGet over there and get her cleaned up, bring her back over here to Dr...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.92,1:33:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他说你叫什么名字？史艳文？ - 史华兹{\r}\N- What he say your name is? Shoots? - Schultz.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.44,1:33:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史华兹{\r}\NSchultz.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.64,1:33:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 把她拖出来，赶快 - 是的{\r}\NGet her back over here. Hurry up, girl. Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.88,1:34:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点，起来{\r}\NCome on, girl. Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.64,1:34:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不要！不要！{\r}\NNo,no!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.44,1:34:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要跟我来？ 还是想睡在那里的地窖？{\r}\NIs you comin' with me or is you gonna sleep in that little box over yonder?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.16,1:36:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}女士们好{\r}\NHello, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.00,1:36:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史医生，容我介绍布希达{\r}\NDr. Schultz. May I introduce to you Broomhilda?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.32,1:36:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}希达，这位是史医生{\r}\NHildi, this is Dr. Schultz.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.16,1:36:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}幸会，布希达{\r}\NIt's a pleasure to meet you, Broomhilda.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.68,1:36:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}久仰大名了{\r}\NI've heard a lot of good things about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.12,1:36:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不是每个黑奴都会说德语，妙吧{\r}\NWell, it's not every nigger speaks German, don't ya know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.04,1:36:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}当我望着你，布希达{\r}\NAs I look at you now, Broomhilda,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.60,1:36:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我能看出你激起的一切热情 完全有理可循{\r}\NI can see all the passions you inspire are completely justified.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.64,1:37:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这位医生会说德语{\r}\NThe doctor here speaks German.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.80,1:37:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我听说你也会说德语？{\r}\NAnd I've been informed you do as well?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.24,1:37:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}露一手，说一点德语{\r}\NGo ahead, girl. Speak a little German.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.76,1:37:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（很荣幸跟您说德语）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.00,1:37:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不是盖的{\r}\NAstonishing.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.12,1:37:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（请进，小姐）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.80,1:37:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我该送来… - 感激不尽{\r}\N- And I shall bring you... - Much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.24,1:37:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（替你倒杯水好吗？){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.60,1:37:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.08,1:38:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别害怕{\r}\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.84,1:38:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（请见谅）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.44,1:38:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（我发觉你很久没说德语了）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.60,1:38:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（所以我会慢慢说）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.72,1:38:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（我跟你说德语只是 以免康迪的人偷听）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.66,1:38:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不好意思{\r}\NPardon.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.60,1:38:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（你很美丽）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.75,1:38:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danke.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.12,1:39:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（我和我们的一个共同朋友）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.56,1:39:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（历经重重困难）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.40,1:39:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（长途跋涉）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.92,1:39:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（为了找你，小姐）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.84,1:39:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（为了解救你）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.00,1:39:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（请喝）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.64,1:39:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（我和我们共同朋友的目的）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.08,1:39:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（就是带你远走高飞）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.60,1:39:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（我没有任何朋友）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.04,1:39:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（有，你有）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.68,1:39:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（谁？){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.04,1:39:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（我不能告诉你）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.20,1:39:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（我们的共同朋友喜欢搞神秘）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.40,1:39:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（这个朋友在哪里？){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.96,1:40:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（就站在那扇门的后方）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.84,1:40:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（答应我你不会尖叫？){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.76,1:40:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（说“我答应”）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.52,1:40:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}嗨，小麻烦{\r}\NHey, Little Trouble Maker.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.08,1:40:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你还真是乌鸦嘴{\r}\NYou silver-tongued devil, you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.44,1:40:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 赶快 - 这些好了，柯拉小姐{\r}\N- Hurry up, girl. - These ready, Miss Cora.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.40,1:40:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不，他们今晚喝酒{\r}\NNo, no, no, they drinkin' tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.92,1:40:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}去楼下拿康迪男士喜欢的大罐红酒{\r}\NGo downstairs, get the big jug with the red stuff Monsieur Candie like, hear?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.92,1:41:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你的俏臀别档路 - 是你的菜吧{\r}\N- Get your big pretty ass out the way. - You know you like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.40,1:41:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你懂我爱什么菜{\r}\NThat's 'cause you knows what I like.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.76,1:41:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快准备好面包{\r}\NCome on with these biscuits, girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.88,1:41:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪男士，他们都是优秀的选手 无庸置疑{\r}\NLook, Monsieur Candie, they were all fine specimens, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.60,1:41:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不过前三名显然是参孙…{\r}\NBut the best three by far were Samson...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.88,1:41:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 另一个叫什么名字？ - 高迪{\r}\N- What's that other one's name? - Goldie.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.16,1:41:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}高迪{\r}\NGoldie.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.36,1:41:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有爱斯基摩乔{\r}\N And Eskimo Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.56,1:41:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对了，为何他叫做爱斯基摩乔？{\r}\NBy the way, why is he called Eskimo Joe?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.32,1:41:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你猜不透黑人的昵称是怎么来的{\r}\NYou never know how these nigger nicknames get started.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.64,1:41:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他名叫乔，或许某天他说他很冷 谁晓得{\r}\NHis name was Joe, maybe one day he said he was cold. Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.08,1:41:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不管怎样，参孙是最强的{\r}\NWell, regardless, Samson's your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.72,1:41:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大家心里有数{\r}\NWe all know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.44,1:41:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你绝不会卖他，我能理解 他是冠军选手{\r}\NYou will never sell him, and I can see why. He's a champion.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.26,1:41:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这三人都是冠军选手{\r}\NAll three are champions.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.68,1:41:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}参孙是冠军选手{\r}\NSamson's the champion.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.92,1:41:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}另两个尚可{\r}\NThem other two pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.00,1:41:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 凯文，这黑人竟敢放肆… - 没关系{\r}\NCalvin, now what's this nigger you let... It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.00,1:42:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你必须了解，康迪男士{\r}\NYou have to understand, Monsieur Candie,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.32,1:42:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}无可否认我是黑人格斗赛的新手{\r}\Nwhile admittedly a neophyte in the nigger fight game,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.88,1:42:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我略有欧洲巡回马戏团的背景{\r}\NI do have a little bit of a background in the European traveling circus.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.28,1:42:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是吗？{\r}\NIs that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.64,1:42:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因此我在甄选上有远大概念{\r}\NHence, I have big ideas when it comes to presentation.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.80,1:42:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我需要的不只是大汉{\r}\NI need something more than just a big nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.20,1:42:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还需要会耍威风{\r}\NYeah, he needs to have panache.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.56,1:42:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 需要什么？ - 耍威风{\r}\N- Need to have what? What? - Panache.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.80,1:42:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 要能招揽顾客的意思 - 招揽顾客，好{\r}\N- A sense of Showmanship. - Showmanship, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.64,1:42:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要能够把他宣传成黑力士{\r}\NI want to be able to bill him as The Black Hercules.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.64,1:42:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 黑力士，太正点了 - 是黑猩猩吧{\r}\NThe Black Hercules, isn't that clever? More like Nigger-les.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.80,1:42:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我引述之前的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.32,1:42:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“我会付最高价买…”{\r}\N"I would pay top dollar for...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.80,1:42:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“独一无二的黑人”{\r}\N'the right nigger."'
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.76,1:42:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不是说爱斯基摩乔本身不好{\r}\NNow I'm not saying that Eskimo Joe is the wrong nigger, per se.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.04,1:42:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但他是独一无二吗？{\r}\NBut is he right as rain?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.92,1:43:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史医生，我敢说黑人格斗赛中{\r}\NOh, Dr. Schultz, I will have you know there is no one in the nigger fight game
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.20,1:43:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没人比我…{\r}\Nthat appreciates the value of showmanship
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.84,1:43:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 更重视招揽顾客 - 没人可比{\r}\Nmore than Monsieur Calvin J. Candie here.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.56,1:43:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但别忘了黑人格斗赛的至高真理{\r}\NNobody. But one must not forget the most important thing in the nigger fight game.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.60,1:43:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}会获胜的黑人最重要{\r}\NAnd that is a nigger that can win fights.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.80,1:43:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那该是你的前几名优先考量{\r}\NNow that should be your first, second, third, fourth, and fifth concern.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.20,1:43:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}先有获胜的黑人{\r}\NNow, after you have that, and you know you have that,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.96,1:43:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你才能开始实行崇高计划{\r}\Nthen you can start to implement a grand design.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.44,1:43:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}换句话说，事情有轻重缓急{\r}\NIn other words, first thing is first.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.32,1:43:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}事情有轻重缓急{\r}\NFirst thing's first.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.46,1:43:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看你们两个很来电{\r}\NI see you two gettin' on.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.56,1:43:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}满意极了{\r}\NFamously.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.80,1:43:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪男士{\r}\NOh, Monsieur Candie,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.12,1:43:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你无法想像四年没听到母语的感觉{\r}\Nyou can't imagine what it's like not to hear your native tongue in four years.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.76,1:43:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我无法想像待在波士顿两周的感觉{\r}\NWell, hell, I can't imagine two weeks in Boston.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.32,1:43:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}待在波士顿两周！ 康迪男士，你超瞎的{\r}\NTwo weeks in Boston! Monsieur Candie, you a mess!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.28,1:43:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}待在波士顿两周！{\r}\NTwo weeks in Boston!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.36,1:44:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我无法表达用母语谈话的喜悦{\r}\NI can't express the joy I felt conversing in my mother tongue.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.64,1:44:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}希达是很迷人的谈话对象{\r}\NAnd Hildi is a charming conversation companion.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.04,1:44:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}小心，史医生{\r}\NWell, be careful now, Dr. Schultz.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.04,1:44:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你可能会变成黑人粉丝{\r}\NYou might-a caught yourself a little dose of nigger love.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.16,1:44:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑人粉丝是很强烈的情绪{\r}\NNigger love's a powerful emotion, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.40,1:44:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就像一池黑沥青 一旦沾上就洗不掉{\r}\NIt's like a pool of black tar. Once it catches your ass, you're caught.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.28,1:44:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是的，会卡住{\r}\NYessir, you stuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.28,1:44:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}医生，我总觉得…{\r}\NI don't know, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.00,1:44:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你尽管用德语的甜言蜜语把妹{\r}\NYou can lay on all the German sweet talk you want,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.12,1:44:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但看来这小妞更属意决哥{\r}\Nbut it looks like this pony's got big eyes for Django.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.24,1:44:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想必如此{\r}\NWell, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.04,1:44:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}威猛的老鹰才能吸引她的注意{\r}\NIt is the soaring eagle that attracts her attention,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.60,1:44:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不是干瘪的小鸡{\r}\Nnot the plucked chicken.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.68,1:44:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史医生，别看轻自己{\r}\NDr. Schultz, don't be so down on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.04,1:44:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你是短小精悍的欧洲绅士{\r}\NYou are quite the dapper European gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.48,1:44:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}盘子洗干净，卖力点，听到没？{\r}\NYou got to clean these dishes, you got to put your elbow in these dishes, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.04,1:44:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你认识那个黑人，对吧？{\r}\NYou know that nigger, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.00,1:44:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 谁？ - 还问谁？{\r}\N- Who? - "Who?"
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.44,1:44:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别唬我，你知道我在说谁{\r}\NDon't "who" me, bitch. You know who I'm talkin' about.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.24,1:45:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那个座上客？{\r}\NAt the table?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.28,1:45:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不认识他{\r}\NI don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.04,1:45:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不认识他{\r}\N- You don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.64,1:45:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 不认识 - 还有呢？{\r}\N- No. - "No," what?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.64,1:45:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没了{\r}\N- No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.52,1:45:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不会骗我吧？{\r}\NYou wouldn't lie to me, now, would you?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.24,1:45:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好{\r}\NOK.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.76,1:45:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你说了算{\r}\NYeah. If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.92,1:45:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}无疑爱斯基摩乔是出色的黑人{\r}\NEskimo Joe's a quality nigger, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.00,1:45:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但如果是我出钱{\r}\NBut if it was my money,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.96,1:45:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不会花12000元买他{\r}\NI wouldn't pay no $12,000 for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.48,1:45:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那你要出什么价？{\r}\NWhat would your price be?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.80,1:45:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要是我情愿当凯子{\r}\NWell, if I was inclined to be generous...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.08,1:45:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不明白为何我情愿当凯子{\r}\Nand I don't know why I would be inclined to be generous...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.40,1:45:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}9000元{\r}\N9,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.60,1:45:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或许{\r}\NMaybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.76,1:45:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史医生{\r}\NDr. Schultz,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.76,1:46:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让我再次澄清 这整场协商的来龙去脉{\r}\Nlet me reclarify how this whole negotiation came about.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.96,1:46:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不是我主动要卖你黑人{\r}\NYou see, it wasn't me who came to you to sell a nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.48,1:46:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}当然不是{\r}\NSure wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.68,1:46:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 是你找上我要买黑人 - 当然是{\r}\NIt was you who approached me to buy one. - Sure was.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.16,1:46:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好小子讨价还价的9000元价码{\r}\N- Now, that $9,000 figure Bright Boy's been bandyin' about,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.76,1:46:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不会相差太远 但要我用这价钱卖爱斯基摩乔{\r}\Nthat ain't too far off from right. And if I wanted to sell Eskimo Joe for that,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.24,1:46:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我无时无刻都能卖 - 随时{\r}\N- I could do so any day of the week. - Any day.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.12,1:46:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但如你在格林维尔所说 我不想卖他{\r}\NBut, like you said in Greenville, doctor... I don't want to sell him.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.80,1:46:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只是你的离谱开价12000元{\r}\NIt was only your ridiculous offer of $12,000
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.12,1:46:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让我甚至考虑一下{\r}\Nthat made me even consider it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.16,1:46:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪男士，你确实富有说服力{\r}\NYou know, Monsieur Candie, you do possess the power of persuasion.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.56,1:46:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有何不可？康迪男士，成交了{\r}\NWhy not? Monsieur Candie, you have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.92,1:46:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}爱斯基摩乔，12000元{\r}\N- Eskimo Joe, $12,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.20,1:46:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}赞啦，医生，明智的决定{\r}\N- Hooray, doctor. Hooray. And a wise decision that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.44,1:46:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然而，那是一笔为数不小的巨款{\r}\NHowever, that is a tremendous amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.28,1:47:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如同你有摩盖先生，我也有律师{\r}\NAnd the way you have your Mr. Moguy, I have a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.48,1:47:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}名叫塔托的锱铢必较哥{\r}\NPersnickety man named Tuttle.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.44,1:47:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我需要塔托先生拟定法律合约{\r}\NAnd I would need my Mr. Tuttle to draw up a legal contract
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.80,1:47:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这样我才安心用大笔钱来换人{\r}\Nbefore I'd feel comfortable exchanging that amount of money for flesh.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.84,1:47:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}更不用说让爱斯基摩乔 给我选定的医生检查{\r}\NNot to mention having Eskimo Joe examined - by a physician of my choosing.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.80,1:47:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 当然了 - 不然等我回来{\r}\N- Naturally. So, say I return in about...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.56,1:47:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}五天后{\r}\N- ...five days time.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.88,1:47:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}五天后？{\r}\N- Five days?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.20,1:47:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}跟塔托先生讨论{\r}\NWith my Mr. Tuttle.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.60,1:47:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然后我的塔托先生与你的摩盖先生{\r}\NAnd then my Mr. Tuttle and your Mr. Moguy
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.08,1:47:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}能乔好彼此之间更繁密的细节{\r}\Ncan hash out the finer details between themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.56,1:47:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我赞成，医生，太赞了{\r}\NI say splendid, doctor. Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.24,1:47:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位{\r}\NGentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.52,1:47:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}容我举杯祝贺{\r}\Nmay I propose a toast.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.80,1:47:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}敬爱斯基摩乔{\r}\NTo Eskimo Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.60,1:47:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或是该称他为黑力士？{\r}\NOr shall we call him The Black Hercules?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.76,1:47:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}敬黑力士{\r}\NTo The Black Hercules.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.84,1:47:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑力士{\r}\NThe Black Hercules.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.60,1:47:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}敬黑力士{\r}\NTo The Black Hercules.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.96,1:47:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你说得对，医生 这称号确实是假掰{\r}\NYou was right, doctor. That name do have pan-ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.56,1:48:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}希达，倒满我的酒杯{\r}\NHildi, top my drink off.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.76,1:48:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}希达，你喜欢在主屋服侍主桌吗？{\r}\NSo, Hildi, how you like servin' at the big table in The Big House?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.92,1:48:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪男士跟你说话就要回答{\r}\NWhen Monsieur Candie talk to you, you answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.28,1:48:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}非常喜欢，康迪男士{\r}\NI like it a lot, Monsieur Candie.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.24,1:48:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}比在热滋滋的地窖里 或被拖过满地荆棘好多了吧{\r}\NIt's a lot better than sizzlin' in that Hot Box or draggin' your ass through a bramble bush.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.84,1:48:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但或许不如取悦曼丁果黑奴 来得有趣吧，甜妞？{\r}\NBut maybe it's not quite as much fun as gettin' to pleasure all them Mandingos,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.80,1:48:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 老天，她喜欢那些黑人，当然了 - 喜欢参孙吗？{\r}\N- Sugar bear? - Oh, Lord, she like them niggers. - Sure do. - Like Samson?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.32,1:48:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不喜欢{\r}\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.56,1:48:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪男士{\r}\NYou know, Monsieur Candie,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.24,1:48:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}医生可能有兴趣看希达的背疤{\r}\Nthe doctor here might be interested in seein' Hildi's peeled back,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.12,1:48:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在他的家乡想必黑人是稀有品种{\r}\Nseein' as how they don't have many niggers where he come from.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.68,1:48:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史医生，你跟希达独处时{\r}\NDr. Schultz, when you was alone with Hildi, here,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.20,1:48:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们只是说德语 还是你有让她卸下衣衫？{\r}\Ndid you just speak German or did you get to take her clothes off?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.56,1:48:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 不，我们只有谈话 - 所以你没看过她的背部？{\r}\NNo, we just talked and... Oh, so you haven't seen her back?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.28,1:48:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我没有…{\r}\N- I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.48,1:48:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不，史提芬说得对 你可能会觉得很有趣{\r}\N- No, no, no, no. Stephen's right, you might find this interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.80,1:48:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}希达，快脱掉衣服{\r}\NHildi, go on, take off your dress.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.40,1:48:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}给史医生看你的背部，赶快{\r}\NShow Dr. Schultz your back here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.56,1:49:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}凯文，我才刚替她着装打扮漂亮{\r}\N- Go on. - Calvin. I just got her all dressed up and lookin' nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.40,1:49:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可是拉拉莉，史医生来自杜塞道夫{\r}\NBut, Lara Lee, Dr. Schultz is from Dusseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.52,1:49:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那里没有黑人 他是学医的{\r}\NThey don't got niggers there. He is a man of medicine.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.56,1:49:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我相信他会迷上黑人的忍痛力{\r}\NI'm sure it would fascinate him, the niggers' endurance for pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.64,1:49:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑人很强悍，无庸置疑{\r}\NThese niggers are tough, Dr. Schultz, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.12,1:49:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}希达的背上被鞭了四下{\r}\NHildi's got somethin' like four lashes on her back.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.36,1:49:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 拉拉莉被鞭一下就会昏倒 - 当然了{\r}\NLara Lee just get one, she'd lose her goddamn mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.32,1:49:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你看，医生，像是图画 - 凯文！{\r}\N- Sure would. - Look at that, doctor. - It's like a paintin'. Look at that. - Calvin!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.24,1:49:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们在用餐 没人想看她背部的鞭痕{\r}\NWe are eating. Ain't no one wanna look at her whipped up back.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.20,1:49:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好吧…{\r}\NFine. Fine, fine, fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.52,1:49:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那晚餐后，史提芬 晚餐后{\r}\NAfter dinner, then, Stephen. After dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.24,1:49:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两位，喝白兰地时再看吧{\r}\NDuring the brandies, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.24,1:49:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}柯拉，带这女孩下去{\r}\NCora, come get this girl!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.32,1:49:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 她的衣服乱掉了 - 是，女士{\r}\N- She a mess. - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.68,1:49:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你怎么衣衫不整？ 我才刚替你打扮好，快进来{\r}\NWhy are you all undone? I just got you done up. Come on in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.04,1:50:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}宝贝，你惹毛史提芬了 你要避开他{\r}\NBaby, you on Stephen bad side, and you need to be on his blind side.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.16,1:50:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你说你不认识他{\r}\NYou say you ain't know him.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.44,1:50:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我说，你说你不认识他{\r}\NI said, you said you ain't know him.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.32,1:50:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不认识{\r}\N- I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.36,1:50:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你认识{\r}\N- Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.88,1:50:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史提芬先生{\r}\NMr. Stephen...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.44,1:50:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不认识{\r}\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.88,1:50:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你为什么骗我？{\r}\NWhy is you lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.48,1:50:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我没有{\r}\NI ain't.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.24,1:50:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那你为什么哭？{\r}\NThen why is you crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.08,1:50:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你吓到我了{\r}\NYou scarin' me.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.12,1:50:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我为什么吓到你了？{\r}\N- Why is I'm scaring you?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.12,1:50:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因为你很可怕{\r}\N- Because you scary.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.56,1:50:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}下午跟希达说德语{\r}\NTo speak German this afternoon with Hildi
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.40,1:50:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}肯定是充实心灵{\r}\Nwas positively soul-enriching.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.28,1:50:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}医生，听了我很窝心{\r}\NDoctor, that warms my heart to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.12,1:50:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你待在这里{\r}\NYou stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.48,1:51:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你之前指出 你愿意割爱希达{\r}\NYou indicated earlier you'd be willing to part with Hildi.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.20,1:51:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，当然好了{\r}\NWhy, yes. Yessiree bob, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.92,1:51:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}既然如此{\r}\NIn that case,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.96,1:51:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}容我提出另一个建议{\r}\Nallow me to propose another proposition.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.12,1:51:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我洗耳恭听{\r}\NI'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.44,1:51:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}赶快，该死{\r}\NHurry up, goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.88,1:51:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 康迪男士 - 史提芬{\r}\N- Monsieur Candie... - Stephen!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.52,1:51:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你刚打断史医生{\r}\NYou just interrupted Dr. Schultz here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.24,1:51:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抱歉，史医生 我的耳朵愈来愈不行了{\r}\NI'm sorry, Dr. Schultz. My ears ain't worth a damn these days.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.24,1:51:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}原谅他{\r}\NExcuse him.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.52,1:51:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪男士，能到厨房说句话吗？{\r}\NMonsieur Candie, could I get a word with you in the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.60,1:51:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你是要我离席？{\r}\NYou mean get up out of my chair?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.64,1:51:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麻烦了{\r}\N- If'n you could manage it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.80,1:51:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 为什么？ - 是甜点的事{\r}\N- Why? - It's about dessert.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.11,1:51:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}甜点怎么了？{\r}\N- What about dessert?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.96,1:51:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我宁可私下讨论{\r}\NI'd rather discuss that in private.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.72,1:51:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们要吃白蛋糕{\r}\NWe're having white cake!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.04,1:51:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}厨房里会出什么乌龙？{\r}\NWhat sort of melodrama could be brewing back there?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.56,1:51:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}您说得是，康迪男士 小的自己处理{\r}\NYou right, Monsieur Candie. You right. I'll handle it myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.04,1:51:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}书房里见{\r}\NMeet me in the library.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.56,1:52:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不懂你干嘛不进来 讨论一下这些黑人{\r}\NI just can't understand why you won't come talk to these niggers.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.08,1:52:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要是出状况，你就怪我{\r}\NShit get fucked up around here, you blame me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.60,1:52:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好啦，史提芬老友，我很快进去{\r}\NFine! Fine. Friend Stephen, I will be along momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.40,1:52:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}了解{\r}\NYessir.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.44,1:52:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两位，如你们所见{\r}\NWell, gentlemen, as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.04,1:52:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}厨房的黑奴手艺绝对一流{\r}\Ntalented as they are, no doubt, in the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.36,1:52:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但偶尔还是需要大人监督{\r}\Nfrom time to time, adult supervision is required.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.76,1:52:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}失陪一下{\r}\NIf you'll excuse me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.68,1:52:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}能清理餐盘了{\r}\NYou may clear the dinner service.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.96,1:52:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}听到没，快去{\r}\NYou heard him. Go on! Get! Hurry up, girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.80,1:52:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}赶快{\r}\NSo,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.00,1:52:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史医生 说个马戏团故事当余兴节目吧{\r}\NDr. Schultz, why don't you regale us with a tale of the circus.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.24,1:52:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马戏团？{\r}\NThe circus?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.32,1:52:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}怎么回事？{\r}\NWhat is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.40,1:53:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那些混蛋不是来买曼丁果黑奴{\r}\NThem motherfuckers ain't here to buy no Mandingos.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.64,1:53:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们想要那个女孩{\r}\NThey wants that girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.28,1:53:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史提芬，你在说什么鬼？{\r}\NStephen, what the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.16,1:53:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是说他们把你当猴耍{\r}\NThey playing your ass for a fool is what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.84,1:53:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们不是来买大只佬黑奴{\r}\NThey ain't here for no musclebound Jimmie.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.92,1:53:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是冲着这女人来的{\r}\NThey here for that girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.36,1:53:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么女孩？希达？{\r}\NWh... What girl? Hildi?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.64,1:53:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，希达，她和决哥是旧识{\r}\NYeah, Hildi. Her and Django, them niggers know each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.92,1:53:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他刚买了爱斯基摩乔{\r}\NHe just bought Eskimo Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.68,1:53:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他付钱了吗？ - 还没，可是…{\r}\N- Did he give you any money? - No! Not yet. But...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.32,1:53:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那他买个屁，还没咧，随便{\r}\NThen he ain't bought diddly. Not yet, nohow.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.84,1:53:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但他正要买…{\r}\NBut he's just about to buy
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.32,1:53:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他意中人的时候被我打断{\r}\Nwho he come here to buy when I interrupted him.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.60,1:53:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“谢谢你，史提芬” 不客气，凯文{\r}\N"Thank you, Stephen." You're welcome, Calvin.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.96,1:53:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你怎么兜在一起的？{\r}\NWhere you gettin' all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.16,1:53:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们何必费尽心机 买一个不值300元的…{\r}\NWhy would they go through all that trouble for a nigger with a chewed up back, ain't worth $300?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.12,1:54:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}瑕疵黑鬼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.40,1:54:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那是因为决哥和希达相爱{\r}\NThey doin' it 'cause that nigger Django's in love with Hildi.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.20,1:54:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她可能是他老婆{\r}\NShe probably his wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.20,1:54:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}至于那个德国人干嘛 帮那个目中无人的王八黑鬼{\r}\NNow, why that German gives a fuck who that uppity son of a bitch
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.26,1:54:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我打死也想不透{\r}\Nis in love with, I'm sure I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.00,1:54:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果她是他们的目标{\r}\NIf she's who they want...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.40,1:54:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那干嘛扯上整个曼丁果？{\r}\Nwhy this whole snake oil pitch about Mandingos, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.84,1:54:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不会鸟300元的交易{\r}\NYou wouldn't pay no never mind to no $300.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.60,1:54:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但12000元呢？{\r}\NBut that 12,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.48,1:54:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让你们变麻吉，对吧？{\r}\N That made you real friendly, now, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.64,1:54:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是啊{\r}\NYes, it did.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.72,1:54:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他老婆，是吗？{\r}\NHis wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.24,1:54:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}既然这么扯，我早该发现的{\r}\NIf it had been a snake, it would have bit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.32,1:54:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那些胡说八道…{\r}\NThose lying...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.16,1:54:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}超浪费时间的…{\r}\Ngoddamn time-wastin'
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.68,1:55:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}王八蛋{\r}\Nsons of bitches.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.20,1:55:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}王八蛋！{\r}\NSons of bitches!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.72,1:55:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我来自纽奥良 所以我很熟悉戏班子{\r}\NOut of New Orleans, so I have quite a bit of practice with theater types.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.16,1:55:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你来了{\r}\NOh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.72,1:55:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我开始以为你和那欧吉桑私奔了{\r}\NI was beginning to think that you and that old crow run off together.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.40,1:55:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那大家会吓死吧{\r}\NThat'd be a hell of a note, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.12,1:55:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拉拉莉，我只是去主窗查看{\r}\NLara Lee, I was just looking out the big window.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.92,1:55:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}比利克莱许在那里应付…{\r}\NBilly Crash is out there dealing with some shady slaver
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.32,1:55:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想卖一群小马的可疑奴隶商 麻烦你去那里检查一下小马{\r}\Ntrying to sell a passel of ponies. Would you be a dear, go out there and give them gals an eyeball?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.44,1:55:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 当然，弟弟 - 谢谢，姊姊{\r}\N- Of course, brother. - Thank you, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.04,1:55:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}做生意全天无休呢{\r}\NYeah. Business never sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.56,1:55:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对了，在你离开之前{\r}\NApropos, before your exit,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.60,1:55:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们在讨论是否能买布希达{\r}\Nwe were discussing the possibility of my purchasing Broomhilda.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.08,1:56:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，没错，医生{\r}\NYes. Yes, we were, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.08,1:56:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等一下再谈{\r}\NAnd we will again. In a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.52,1:56:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的这个小朋友是谁？{\r}\NWho's your little friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.72,1:56:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是班{\r}\NThis is Ben.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.56,1:56:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他是住在这里很久的老仆人{\r}\NHe's a old Joe that lived around here for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.72,1:56:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是真的久到不行{\r}\NAnd I do mean a long damn time.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.32,1:56:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老班照顾我爸{\r}\NOld Ben here took care of my daddy...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.76,1:56:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有我爷爷{\r}\Nand my daddy's daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.08,1:56:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}直到他有一天暴毙{\r}\NTill he up and keeled over one day...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.48,1:56:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老班也照顾我{\r}\NOld Ben took care of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.60,1:56:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是密西西比大庄园主人的儿子{\r}\NGrowing up the son of a huge plantation owner in Mississippi
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.84,1:57:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}见过…{\r}\Nputs a white man
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.84,1:57:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一脱拉库的黑人{\r}\Nin contact with a whole lotta black faces.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.28,1:57:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我这辈子都生活在这里 就在这里糖果园{\r}\NI spent my whole life here, right here in Candyland...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.88,1:57:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}身边全是黑人{\r}\Nsurrounded by black faces.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.60,1:57:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}每天看到他们，日复一日{\r}\NNow, seeing them every day, day in, day out,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.12,1:57:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我只有一个问题{\r}\NI only had one question:
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.92,1:57:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们为何不出草杀光白人？{\r}\NWhy don't they kill us?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.52,1:57:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在那里的阳台 50年来每周3次{\r}\NNow, right out there on that porch, three times a week for 50 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.76,1:57:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老班会用利刀替我爸刮胡子{\r}\NOld Ben here would shave my daddy with a straight razor.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.16,1:57:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果我是老班 我早就给我老爸割喉了{\r}\NNow, if I was Old Ben, I woulda cut my daddy's goddamn throat
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.24,1:57:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}而且根本不必犹豫50年{\r}\Nand it wouldn't have taken me no 50 years to do it, neither.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.20,1:57:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但他从没有{\r}\NBut he never did.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.60,1:58:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}为何没有？{\r}\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.24,1:58:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}瞧，颅相学{\r}\NYou see, the science of phrenology
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.20,1:58:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可有效理解…{\r}\Nis crucial to understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.56,1:58:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑人和白人的差异{\r}\Nthe separation of our two species.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.12,1:58:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在这个黑人的头骨中{\r}\NIn the skull of the African here,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.88,1:58:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}攸关服从的部位{\r}\Nthe area associated with submissiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.60,1:58:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}比地球上任何人类 或任何其他动物都来得大{\r}\Nis larger than any human or any other subhuman species on planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.32,1:58:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果你检查…{\r}\NIf you examine...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.56,1:58:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这片头骨{\r}\Nthis piece of skull here...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.04,1:58:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你会注意到三处明显的凹洞{\r}\Nyou will notice three distinct dimples.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.16,1:59:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这里、这里和这里{\r}\NHere, here and here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.24,1:59:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在{\r}\NNow...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.60,1:59:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果我拿的是牛顿或伽利咯的头骨{\r}\Nif I was holding the skull of an Isaac Newton or Galileo,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.64,1:59:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这三处凹洞会出现在 头骨最攸关什么的部位{\r}\Nthese three dimples would be found in the area of the skull
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.39,1:59:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}创造力{\r}\Nmost associated with... creativity.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.20,1:59:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但这是老班的头骨{\r}\NBut this is the skull of Old Ben.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.96,1:59:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在老班的头骨中{\r}\NAnd in the skull of Old Ben,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.00,1:59:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天资匮乏{\r}\Nunburdened by genius,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.44,1:59:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这三处凹洞存在于 头骨最攸关什么的部位{\r}\Nthese three dimples exist in the area of the skull most associated with...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.76,1:59:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}奴性{\r}\Nservility.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.28,1:59:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好小子{\r}\NNow, Bright Boy...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.76,1:59:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我承认你很聪明{\r}\NI will admit you are pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.48,1:59:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但如果我拿这支榔头{\r}\NBut if I took this hammer here...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.72,1:59:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}猛槌你的头骨{\r}\Nand I bashed in your skull with it...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.08,1:59:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在相同的部位 也有三处相同的凹洞{\r}\Nyou would have the same three dimples in the same place...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.64,1:59:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}跟老班一样{\r}\Nas Old Ben.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.32,1:59:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在把手掌摊平在桌上{\r}\NHey! Now lay your palms flat on that tabletop!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.96,2:00:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只要你们的手掌离闭那张龟壳桌{\r}\NIf you lift those palms off that turtle shell tabletop,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:03.12,2:00:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布奇先生就会用短枪轰了你们{\r}\NMr. Pooch is gonna let loose with both barrels of that sawed-off.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.52,2:00:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}今晚宴席问鬼话连篇{\r}\NThere have been a lot of lies said around this dinner table here tonight,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.08,2:00:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但现在是来真的{\r}\Nbut that you can believe!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.36,2:00:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}摩盖先生 麻烦收走挂在他们腰际的枪{\r}\NMr. Moguy, would you be so kind as to collect the pistol hanging off these boys' hips here?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.24,2:00:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 非常感谢 - 医生{\r}\N- Thank you ever so much. - Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.32,2:00:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}讲到哪里了？{\r}\NWhere were we?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.16,2:00:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}驴蛋{\r}\NJackass.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.44,2:00:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想到了{\r}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.24,2:00:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我相信你们正准备提案…{\r}\NI do believe you were just getting ready to make me
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.96,2:00:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}买布希达{\r}\Na proposition to buy Broomhilda.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.80,2:00:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对吧？{\r}\NAm I right?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:54.20,2:00:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对{\r}\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.64,2:00:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把希达带出来{\r}\NBring out Hildi!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.32,2:01:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}过去那里{\r}\NGet over there yonder.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.08,2:01:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}给我坐在椅子上{\r}\NSit your ass in that goddamn...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.64,2:01:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 把手摊平在桌上 - 闭嘴{\r}\NLay your hand flat on that tabletop. Now shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.88,2:01:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史医生{\r}\NDr. Schultz, in Greenville,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.32,2:01:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在格林维尔 你自己说“独一无二的黑人”{\r}\Nyou yourself said that for the right nigger
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.36,2:01:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你愿意出公认的离谱价钱{\r}\Nyou'd be willin' to pay what some may consider is a ridiculous amount.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.04,2:01:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}而我问“你怎么定义离谱”{\r}\NTo which me myself said, "What is your definition of ridiculous?"
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.56,2:01:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你回答“12000元”{\r}\NTo which you said, "$12,000."
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.04,2:01:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}既然你们千里迢迢{\r}\NNow, considering y'all have ridden a whole lot of miles,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.88,2:01:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}经历这么多困难{\r}\Nwent through a whole lot of trouble, and done spread a whole lot of bull
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.20,2:01:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}瞎掰这么多谎话 只为了买这个俏妞{\r}\Nto purchase this lovely lady right here,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.68,2:01:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}显然布希达其实才是 “独一无二的黑人”{\r}\Nit would appear that Broomhilda is, in fact... the right nigger.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:49.92,2:01:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果你们想要 带着布希达离开糖果园{\r}\NAnd if y'all want to leave Candyland with Broomhilda,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.84,2:01:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}价钱就是12000元{\r}\Nthe price is $12,000.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.52,2:02:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我猜你偏好 “不要就拉倒”的协商风格{\r}\NAnd I take it you prefer the "take it or leave it" style of negotiation?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.56,2:02:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没错，医生{\r}\NYes, I do, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.96,2:02:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}按照契卡索郡的法律{\r}\NYou see, under the laws of Chickasaw County,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.04,2:02:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布希达是我的财产{\r}\NBroomhilda here is my property.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.72,2:02:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我能对我的财产随心所欲{\r}\NAnd I can choose to do with my property whatever I so desire!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.08,2:02:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果你们认为…{\r}\NAnd if y'all think my price...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.08,2:02:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这个黑人的索价太高{\r}\Nfor this nigger here is too steep...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.84,2:02:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的随心所欲说是…{\r}\Nwhat I'm gonna desire to do is...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.04,2:02:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}用这支榔头把她槌死{\r}\Ntake this goddamn hammer here and beat her ass to death with it!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.72,2:02:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就在你们两人面前{\r}\N- Right in front of both y'all!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:39.40,2:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}冷静，大块头{\r}\N- Easy, big fella.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.68,2:02:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那样我们就能检查 布希达的头骨里有没有三个凹洞{\r}\NThen we can examine the three dimples inside Broomhilda's skull!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.64,2:02:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}医生，你的决定怎样？{\r}\NNow, what's it gonna be, doc?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.28,2:02:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的决定怎样？{\r}\NWhat's it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.64,2:02:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我能把手离开桌上 拿出我的皮夹吗？{\r}\NMay I lift the hands off the tabletop in order to remove my billfold?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.48,2:02:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请便{\r}\NYes, you may.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:10.52,2:03:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是12000元{\r}\NThat 12.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:15.80,2:03:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}售出{\r}\NSold!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.96,2:03:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}卖给好样的胡子男 还有他好样的黑人{\r}\NTo the man with the exceptional beard and his unexceptional nigger.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.68,2:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 摩盖先生 - 是，凯文{\r}\N- Mr. Moguy. - Yes, Calvin?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.72,2:03:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请开12000元的收据给这两位男士{\r}\NWill you make these gentlemen a receipt for $12,000, please?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.16,2:03:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}12000元{\r}\N$12,000.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:41.00,2:03:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很高兴跟你们做生意{\r}\NIt was a pleasure doing business with y'all.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.00,2:03:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两位{\r}\NNow, gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.84,2:03:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}欢迎一起来客厅{\r}\Nif you care to join me in the parlor...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:49.88,2:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们要上白蛋糕了{\r}\Nwe will be serving white cake.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.24,2:04:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（布希达冯夏夫）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.80,2:05:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（凯文康迪，李奥奈摩盖）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.52,2:05:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}干得好，凯文{\r}\NWell done, Calvin.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.40,2:05:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请暂停{\r}\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.88,2:05:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请暂停，女士{\r}\NExcuse me, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.64,2:05:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请停止弹贝多芬了{\r}\NCould you please stop playing Beethoven?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.20,2:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}手别碰竖琴了{\r}\NTake your hands off the harp!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.64,2:05:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}医生{\r}\NDoctor!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.32,2:05:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 医生，你不能进去 - 史提芬，史提芬{\r}\N- Doctor, you can't go in there! - Stephen, Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.08,2:05:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他没事干嘛进去 - 不要紧{\r}\NHe ain't got no business going in there. Let it be.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.00,2:05:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他只是有点郁闷，我来搞定{\r}\NHe's just a little upset, that's all. I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.04,2:06:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}吃白蛋糕？{\r}\NWhite cake?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:15.20,2:06:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不嗜吃甜食，谢谢{\r}\NI don't go in for sweets, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:27.32,2:06:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在思索我怎么打败你的？{\r}\NYou brooding about me getting the best of you?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.84,2:06:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}其实我在想 你今天喂狗的那个可怜鬼{\r}\NActually, I was thinking of that poor devil you fed to the dogs today.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.92,2:06:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}达太安{\r}\ND'Artagnan.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.52,2:06:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我很纳闷大仲马会做何感想{\r}\NAnd I was wondering what Dumas would make of all this.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.48,2:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再说一次？{\r}\NCome again?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.04,2:06:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}亚历山大仲马 《三剑客》的作者{\r}\NAlexandre Dumas. He wrote The Three Musketeers.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.28,2:06:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是啊，医生{\r}\NYes, of course, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:53.00,2:06:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想你一定是他的书迷{\r}\NI figured you must be an admirer.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.88,2:06:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你以他小说的主角给奴隶命名{\r}\NYou named your slave after his novel's lead character.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:59.40,2:07:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果今天大仲马在场{\r}\NNow, if Alexandre Dumas had been there today,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.96,2:07:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我很纳闷大仲马会做何感想{\r}\NI wonder what he would have made of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:07.32,2:07:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你怀疑他不会认同？{\r}\NYou doubt he'd approve?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.20,2:07:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，他认同的话绝对令人匪夷所思{\r}\NYes. His approval would be a dubious proposition at best.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.72,2:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}软心肠的法国人{\r}\NSoft-hearted Frenchie.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.40,2:07:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大仲马有黑人血统{\r}\NAlexandre Dumas is black.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.40,2:07:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 这是布希达的合约吗？ - 没错{\r}\N- Are these Broomhilda's papers? - Yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.44,2:07:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我能检查吗？ - 当然{\r}\N- May I? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:33.28,2:07:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.80,2:07:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那是她的卖契、历年主人{\r}\NThat is her bill of sale, her ownership history,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:39.68,2:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}当然还有她的自由证明{\r}\Nand, of course, her freedom papers, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:42.24,2:07:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有笔和墨水借我吗？{\r}\NWould you have ink and pen for me?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:45.60,2:07:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 在那个小桌上 - 谢谢{\r}\N- Right over there on that little table. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:10.00,2:08:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.68,2:08:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布希达冯夏夫{\r}\NBroomhilda Von Shaft...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.12,2:08:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你已经是自由的女人了{\r}\Nconsider yourself a free woman.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:33.48,2:08:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康迪先生{\r}\NMr. Candie...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.28,2:08:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}通常，我会说“再会”{\r}\Nnormally, I would say auf Wiedersehen.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.32,2:08:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但因为“再会”的真正意思是 “后会有期”{\r}\NBut since what auf Wiedersehen actually means is "till I see you again"
Dialogue: 0,2:08:46.12,2:08:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}既然我绝不愿再见到你 对你…{\r}\Nand since I never wish to see you again,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.55,2:08:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我会说“永别了”{\r}\Nto you, sir... I say, "goodbye."
Dialogue: 0,2:08:57.04,2:08:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}走吧{\r}\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:59.60,2:09:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}来吧{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.88,2:09:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等一下，医生{\r}\NOne more moment, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:06.56,2:09:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么事？{\r}\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.32,2:09:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}南方这里有个传统{\r}\NIt's a custom here in the South...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.04,2:09:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一旦交易结束，双方会握手{\r}\Nonce a business deal is concluded that the two parties shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:21.24,2:09:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 意味着诚意 - 我不是南方人{\r}\NIt implies good faith. - I'm not from the South.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:23.38,2:09:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但是你…{\r}\N - But you are...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.68,2:09:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在我家里，医生{\r}\Nin my house, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:29.76,2:09:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}恐怕我得坚持{\r}\N- So I'm afraid I must insist.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:31.64,2:09:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}坚持？{\r}\N- Insist?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.84,2:09:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}坚持什么？我跟你握手？{\r}\NOn what? That I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:35.16,2:09:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那恐怕我得坚持与你作对{\r}\NOh, then I'm afraid I must insist in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.96,2:09:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 知道我怎么看你？ - 你怎么看我？不知道{\r}\N- You know what I think you are? - What you think I am? No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.36,2:09:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看你是输不起{\r}\N- I think you are a bad loser.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:47.88,2:09:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看你是赢得不光彩{\r}\N- And I think you're an abysmal winner.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.12,2:09:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然而{\r}\NNevertheless,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.96,2:09:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在契卡索郡，交易不算完成{\r}\N here in Chickasaw County, a deal ain't done
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.28,2:09:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}除非双方握手{\r}\Nuntil the two parties have shook hands.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.36,2:10:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}即使签了所有合约也不算{\r}\NEven after all that paper signin', don't mean shit...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:03.36,2:10:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你没跟我握手{\r}\Nyou don't shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.72,2:10:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果我没跟你握手 你会舍弃12000元？{\r}\NIf I don't shake your hand, you're gonna throw away $12,000?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.76,2:10:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我认为不会{\r}\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:16.56,2:10:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布奇先生{\r}\NMr. Pooch?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.60,2:10:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这个哈黑鬼的德国人跟我握手前 如果她想离开这里{\r}\NIf she tries to leave here before this nigger-loving German shakes my hand,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.40,2:10:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你就毙了她{\r}\Nyou cut her ass down.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:48.04,2:10:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你真想要我跟你握手？{\r}\NYou really want me to shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.00,2:10:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我坚持{\r}\NI insist.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:55.88,2:10:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}既然你坚持{\r}\NIf you insist.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:15.08,2:11:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不！凯文！{\r}\NNo! Calvin!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.20,2:11:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}凯文！{\r}\NCalvin!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:27.00,2:11:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抱歉，我控制不了{\r}\NI'm sorry. I couldn't resist.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.92,2:11:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑人抓狂了！救命！{\r}\NNi99er's gone crazy! Help!
