Dialogue: 0,2:12:10.64,2:12:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可恶，妈的{\r}\NDamn it! Fuckin'...!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.28,2:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}搞屁{\r}\NGet the...!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:16.48,2:12:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可恶，王八蛋，搞啥{\r}\NDamn it, son of a bitch! What...?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:19.28,2:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天杀的黑鬼{\r}\NFucking...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.72,2:12:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可恶{\r}\NGoddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:22.76,2:12:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}搞什么鬼？{\r}\NWhat the fuck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:25.68,2:12:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你射到我了{\r}\NYou shot me!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:27.36,2:12:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你这猪脑袋{\r}\N- You stupid son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:29.04,2:12:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抱歉，杰西{\r}\N- Sorry, Jessie!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:30.60,2:12:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谁居然给黑人枪？{\r}\NWho the fuck gave a nigger a goddamn gun?
