Dialogue: 0,2:13:08.76,2:13:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑鬼！我要杀了你！{\r}\NNigger! Gonna kill...!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.52,2:13:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天啊，我的天啊{\r}\NGod! Oh, my God!
