Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.28,2:14:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可恶{\r}\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:35.56,2:14:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}停火！{\r}\NHold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:40.40,2:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}停火！{\r}\NHold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:43.84,2:14:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别开枪了，该死{\r}\NStop shootin', goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.28,2:14:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥{\r}\NDjango!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:56.16,2:14:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么？{\r}\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.32,2:15:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们抓到你的女人{\r}\NWe got your woman!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:03.40,2:15:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}比利克莱许的枪顶着她的头{\r}\NBilly Crash here got his pistol upside her head.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:06.88,2:15:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你再不停止屠杀 他会轰了她的头{\r}\NYou don't stop all that carrying on, he gonna blow her goddamn brains out.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.16,2:15:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这不只是威胁，骑马仔{\r}\NAnd that ain't no threat, horse boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:14.52,2:15:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是保证{\r}\NThat there is a promise.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:17.48,2:15:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或是…{\r}\NOr...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.08,2:15:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你能投降，缴械{\r}\Nyou can give up, throw your gun out...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.00,2:15:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们就不会杀希达{\r}\N- ...we won't kill Hildi.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:24.48,2:15:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}狗屁{\r}\N- Horseshit!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:26.04,2:15:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}说真的，决哥，我对天发誓{\r}\NHonest lnjun, Django. I swear 'fore God.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:30.20,2:15:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你投降{\r}\NYou give up,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:32.16,2:15:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她就不会受到伤害{\r}\Nain't no harm gonna come to her.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.32,2:15:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我该相信你这黑鬼吗？{\r}\NAnd I'm supposed to believe your black ass?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:38.76,2:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就我个人，我才不鸟你相不相信{\r}\NPersonally, I don't give a good goddamn what you believe or don't believe!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:41.92,2:15:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我相信你10秒内不投降{\r}\NI believe if you don't give up in the next ten seconds,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.04,2:15:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们会把这女人的头轰掉 你最好相信{\r}\Nwe gonna blow this bitch's brains out! Believe that!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:51.28,2:15:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不要{\r}\NDon't do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:53.24,2:15:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不要管我{\r}\NYou give me up.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:55.20,2:15:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 6 !    - 别管我{\r}\N- Six! - Just let me go.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:57.20,2:15:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 7 !  - 他们夺走太多了{\r}\N- Seven! - They got too much.
