Dialogue: 0,2:18:14.96,2:18:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}该醒了，黑鬼{\r}\NCock-a-doodle-do, nigger.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:22.28,2:18:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们是赏金猎人，是吧？{\r}\NSo y'all bounty hunters?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:25.48,2:18:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我就知道你们很可疑{\r}\NI knew there was something fishy about y'all.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:29.16,2:18:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们在你们的鞍囊中{\r}\NWe found your wanted posters...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:31.88,2:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}发现通缉令和帐簿{\r}\Nand book of figures in your saddlebags.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:35.68,2:18:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我得说{\r}\NI got to say...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:38.24,2:18:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我之前从没听过黑人的赏金猎人{\r}\NI ain't never heard of no black bounty hunter before.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:41.60,2:18:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑人收钱杀白人？这啥台词啊{\r}\NBlack boy paid to kill white men? How'd you like that line of work?
