Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.58,2:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}冷静，好戏要登场了{\r}\NCalm down, now, here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:09.96,2:19:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}领班{\r}\N" Captain?"
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.64,2:19:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拉拉小姐要见你{\r}\NMiss Lara want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:14.12,2:19:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要讨论主人的葬礼事宜{\r}\NSomething to do with the Old Man's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:18.48,2:19:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她改变主意不阉决哥了{\r}\NOh, and she changed her mind 'bout snipping Django.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:23.08,2:19:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她要把他交给雷昆迪基的人{\r}\NShe gonna give him to the LeQuint Dickey people.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.64,2:19:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她讲得这么临时{\r}\NWell, she didn't waste a minute telling me.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:36.96,2:19:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}令人大失所望{\r}\NHow disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:01.80,2:20:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要走了{\r}\NYou leavin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:04.88,2:20:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你能带走这些{\r}\NThis here what you take with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:11.28,2:20:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你这黑鬼的事迹让主屋那群人…{\r}\NYour black ass has been all them motherfuckers at The Big House
Dialogue: 0,2:20:15.00,2:20:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}议论纷纷好几小时{\r}\Ncould talk about for the last few hours.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:18.44,2:20:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好像白人这辈子只会把头脑用在…{\r}\NSeem like white folk ain't never had a bright idea in they life
Dialogue: 0,2:20:22.12,2:20:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想出杀你的各种方法{\r}\Nwas coming up with all kinds of ways to kill your ass.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:25.28,2:20:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}提醒你 多数点子都跟乱搞你的小弟弟有关{\r}\NNow, mind you, most of them ideas had to do with fuckin' with your fun parts.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.68,2:20:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那似乎是个好点子{\r}\NNow, that may seem like a good idea,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:34.56,2:20:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但实际上{\r}\Nbut truth is...
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.72,2:20:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}当黑人被阉了{\r}\Nwhen you snip a nigger's nuts,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:40.40,2:20:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}多数人会在7分钟内流血至死{\r}\Nmost of them bleed out in, oh, about, hm... seven minutes.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:44.68,2:20:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}多数人{\r}\NMost of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.35,2:20:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}绝大多数{\r}\NWell, more than most.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:50.20,2:20:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然后我说{\r}\NThen I says:
Dialogue: 0,2:20:53.44,2:20:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“屁啦”{\r}\N"Shitfire."
Dialogue: 0,2:20:56.24,2:21:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“我们卖给雷昆迪基的黑人比那更惨”{\r}\NThe niggers we sell to LeQuint Dickey got it worse than that."
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.24,2:21:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们继续说“把他鞭死”{\r}\NAnd they still sayin', "Let's whip him to death."
Dialogue: 0,2:21:04.12,2:21:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“把他丢进曼丁果格斗 把他喂史东赛佛的狗”{\r}\NOr "Throw him to the Mandingos." "Feed him to Stonesipher's dogs."
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.76,2:21:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我说“那又什么特别”{\r}\NAnd I said, "What's so special about that?"
Dialogue: 0,2:21:11.20,2:21:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“我们经常那样搞”{\r}\NWe do that shit all the time.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:13.28,2:21:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“那敢情好”{\r}\N"Hell's bells,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:14.52,2:21:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“我们卖给雷昆迪基的黑人比那更惨”{\r}\Nthe niggers we sell to LeQuint Dickey got it worse than that."
Dialogue: 0,2:21:20.36,2:21:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}阿娘喂{\r}\NLo and behold,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:23.36,2:21:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}突然拉拉小姐想出一个妙计{\r}\Nout of nowhere, Miss Lara come up with the bright idea
Dialogue: 0,2:21:28.16,2:21:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把你交给雷昆迪基矿业公司{\r}\Nof giving your ass to the LeQuint Dickey Mining Company.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:34.24,2:21:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}作为雷昆迪基矿业公司的奴隶{\r}\NAnd as a slave of the LeQuint Dickey Mining Company,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:39.32,2:21:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}今后，直到你吗屁那天{\r}\Nhenceforth, till the day you die,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:43.08,2:21:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}整天，每天{\r}\Nall day, every day,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:46.28,2:21:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你会挥着大锤{\r}\Nyou will be swinging a sledgehammer,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:49.32,2:21:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把大石头敲成小石子{\r}\Nturning big rocks into little rocks.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:54.44,2:21:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你到了那里{\r}\NNow, when you get there,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:56.08,2:21:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们会夺去你的名字{\r}\Nthey gonna take away your name,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:58.84,2:22:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}给你一个编号和大锤{\r}\Ngive you a number and a sledgehammer,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:02.12,2:22:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对你喊“干活了”{\r}\Nand say, "Get to work!"
Dialogue: 0,2:22:04.52,2:22:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一反嘴，舌头说被割掉{\r}\NOne word of sass, they cuts out your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:07.24,2:22:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们也很拿手，你不会流血至死{\r}\NAnd they good at it too. You won't bleed out.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:09.84,2:22:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真的很拿手{\r}\NThey does that real good.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:13.44,2:22:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们会操死你{\r}\NThey gonna work ya.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:15.20,2:22:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}整天，每天，直到你再也不行{\r}\NAll day, every day, till your back give out.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:20.40,2:22:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们就会用榔头砸你的头{\r}\NThen they're gonna hit you in the head with a hammer,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:23.40,2:22:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把你丢到黑鬼洞{\r}\Nthrow your ass down the nigger hole.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:25.68,2:22:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这就是你的一生，决哥{\r}\NAnd that will be the story of you, Django.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:33.96,2:22:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（往雷昆迪基矿业公司的途中）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.76,2:23:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}法兰基，指导原则是什么？{\r}\NAnd what's the golden rule, Frankie?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:12.64,2:23:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不跟土著打炮{\r}\NYou don't root abos.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:19.80,2:23:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}白人小子{\r}\NHey, white boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:22.76,2:23:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我在叫你，白人小子{\r}\NI said, hey, white boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:25.12,2:23:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}闭嘴，黑人 我对你想说的话兴趣缺缺{\r}\NShut up, black. You ain't got nothing to say I want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:28.40,2:23:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你想赚11000元吗？{\r}\NHow'd you like to make $11,000?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:30.80,2:23:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在说啥？{\r}\NDo what, now?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:32.08,2:23:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我说你想赚11000元吗？{\r}\NI said how'd you like to make $11,000?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:35.96,2:23:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 其实是11500元 - 你在说什么鬼？{\r}\N 11,500, actually. What the fuck are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:40.28,2:23:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在刚才的糖果园庄园 有11500元的巨款{\r}\NBack there at that plantation, Candyland, there was an $11,500 fortune,
Dialogue: 0,2:23:45.16,2:23:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就摆在那里，你们都错过了{\r}\Njust sittin' there. And y'all rode right past it.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:48.40,2:23:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}去你的，黑仔，我们不是强盗{\r}\NYou be damned, blackie, we're not bandits.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:50.76,2:23:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没叫你抢 这笔巨款的好处就是不违法{\r}\NI ain't saying that. Nice thing about this fortune is it ain't illegal.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:55.16,2:23:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不能用偷的 要用挣的，白人小子{\r}\NYou can't steal it. You got to earn it, white boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:59.28,2:24:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有话快说，有屁快放{\r}\NYou got something to say, mate, you say it.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:01.68,2:24:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}11500元巨款在糖果园等你{\r}\NThe $11,500 fortune waitin' for you back at Candyland
Dialogue: 0,2:24:04.76,2:24:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}形式就是史密提毕考帮…{\r}\Nis in the form of a "Wanted Dead or Alive" bounty
Dialogue: 0,2:24:07.76,2:24:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- “无论生死通缉令”的赏金 - 史密提毕考是什么人？{\r}\Non Smitty Bacall and the Bacall Gang. Who the fuck is Smitty Bacall?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:11.76,2:24:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史密提毕考是火车劫杀帮派 史密提毕考帮的头目{\r}\NSmitty Bacall is the leader of this murderous gang of stagecoach robbers, the Bacall Gang.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:16.56,2:24:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}杀了他有7000元赏金{\r}\NThere's a $7,000 "Wanted Dead or Alive" bounty on him,
Dialogue: 0,2:24:19.96,2:24:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他的三个共犯每个1500元{\r}\N$1,500 for each of his three accomplices:
Dialogue: 0,2:24:23.40,2:24:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}丹尼麦可斯{\r}\NDandy Michaels,
Dialogue: 0,2:24:25.28,2:24:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}杰拉德纳许和疯子克雷格库恩{\r}\NGerald Nash, and Crazy Craig Koons.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:29.56,2:24:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们全部四人{\r}\NNow, all four of them gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,2:24:31.24,2:24:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}正在糖果园里狂笑，知道原因？{\r}\Nthey back there at Candyland laughing their ass off.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:33.58,2:24:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因为他们逃过谋杀罪了 但他们不会得逞{\r}\NYou know why? 'Cause they just got away with murder. But it ain't got to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:39.04,2:24:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你和你同伴 你们能回去挣那笔钱{\r}\NYou and your mates, y'all can ride back there and y'all can go get that money.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:42.68,2:24:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你说这些败类干了什么？ - 这些王八蛋滥杀无辜{\r}\NWhat'd these jokers do again? These sons of bitches, they killed innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:47.44,2:24:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马车抢劫，杀无辜白人{\r}\NStagecoach robbery. Innocent white people.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:51.72,2:24:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的口袋里有传单，能拿给你{\r}\NI got the handbill right here in my pocket, if you let me get it.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:55.28,2:24:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拿出来{\r}\NGet it out.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:58.08,2:25:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“通缉，无论生死 史密提毕考…”{\r}\N"Wanted. Dead or alive. Smitty Bacall
Dialogue: 0,2:25:01.16,2:25:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- “和史密提毕考同伙” - 但你是奴隶{\r}\Nand the Smitty Bacall Gang." - But you're a slave.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:04.08,2:25:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- “因谋杀…” - 我才不是奴隶{\r}\N- "For murder..." - I ain't no goddamn slave.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:06.24,2:25:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“和马车抢劫”{\r}\N- "...and stagecoach robbery."
Dialogue: 0,2:25:07.52,2:25:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的口气像奴隶吗？{\r}\NDo I sound like a fuckin' slave?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:09.28,2:25:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- “7000元悬赏史密提毕考” - 一大笔钱耶{\r}\N"$7,000 for Smitty Bacall." - That's a shitload.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:10.74,2:25:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是赏金猎人{\r}\N - I'm a bounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:14.76,2:25:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昨天，我是自由民{\r}\NYesterday, as a free man,
Dialogue: 0,2:25:17.64,2:25:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我与我的德国白人伙伴 骑马来到糖果园{\r}\NI rode into Candyland on a horse with my German white partner,
Dialogue: 0,2:25:22.44,2:25:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}金史华兹医生{\r}\NDr. King Schultz.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:24.12,2:25:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们从德州一路追踪 史密提毕考帮到契卡索郡{\r}\NWe tracked the Bacall Gang all the way from Texas to Chickasaw County.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:29.08,2:25:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}终于发现他们躲在糖果园{\r}\NWe finally found their ass layin' low in Candyland.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.04,2:25:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们进去抓他们，但情况生变{\r}\NWe went in there to get 'em, things went sour,
Dialogue: 0,2:25:35.64,2:25:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的伙伴被杀，凯文康迪中弹{\r}\Nmy partner got killed, Calvin Candie got shot,
Dialogue: 0,2:25:39.20,2:25:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}全庄园的人决定要怪罪我{\r}\Nthen everybody there decided to blame me,
Dialogue: 0,2:25:42.00,2:25:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我就沦落这地步{\r}\N so here I am.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:45.28,2:25:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我不该在运送名单上{\r}\NBut y'all know I ain't on that manifest.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:47.56,2:25:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不该被拖上这趟旅途{\r}\NAnd all y'all know I ain't supposed to be on this trip.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:50.56,2:25:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但他们四人仍在那里，仍受通缉{\r}\NBut them four men is still back there, they're still wanted,
Dialogue: 0,2:25:54.00,2:25:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那是唾手可得的11500元{\r}\Nand that 11,500 is up for grabs, and the last thing they'd expect
Dialogue: 0,2:25:56.00,2:25:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们打死料不到你们这记回马枪{\r}\Nis y'all ridin' back in there and gettin' it.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:00.04,2:26:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在盘算什么？{\r}\NWhat's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:01.84,2:26:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你供出他们是谁，我们放你走？{\r}\NYou tell us who they are and we turn you loose?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:05.52,2:26:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不，我不会供出他们是谁{\r}\NNo, no, no, no. I ain't gonna tell you who they are.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:08.44,2:26:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}除非你给我一把枪、一匹马{\r}\NBut, you give me a pistol, one of them horses,
Dialogue: 0,2:26:11.96,2:26:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有11500元分我500元 我就会指出他们{\r}\Nand $500 of that 11,500, and I'll point 'em out to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:16.80,2:26:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是如假包换的传单{\r}\NThis is a real handbill.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:18.32,2:26:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就算传单是真的 不代表他没在胡说{\r}\NNow just 'cause it's a real handbill doesn't mean that other bunch of malarkey is.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:22.64,2:26:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}为什么奴隶口袋里会有…{\r}\NNow why would a slave have a
Dialogue: 0,2:26:24.60,2:26:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“无论生死通缉令”传单？{\r}\N"Wanted Dead or Alive" handbill in his pocket?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:32.84,2:26:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那个黑人昨天骑进糖果园？{\r}\NDid that black ride into Candyland yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:42.04,2:26:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好，我再问你们一次{\r}\NAll right, I'm gonna ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:47.20,2:26:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}切记，我不喜欢有人说谎{\r}\NI want you to remember, I don't like liars.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:50.56,2:26:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他是糖果园的奴隶{\r}\NIs he a Candyland slave,
Dialogue: 0,2:26:52.44,2:26:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还是他昨天跟个白人骑马来？{\r}\Nor did he ride in with a white man on a horse yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:56.44,2:26:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对{\r}\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:58.44,2:27:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们从格林维尔拍卖会就随行{\r}\NThey walked us from the Greenville auction,
Dialogue: 0,2:27:00.92,2:27:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他跟个白人骑马来{\r}\Nand he rode in on a horse with a white man.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:03.68,2:27:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这个黑人是那白人的奴隶吗？{\r}\NNow this white man, was the black his slave?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.00,2:27:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他不是奴隶{\r}\NHe weren't no slave.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:09.68,2:27:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你百分之百确定？{\r}\N- You fuckin' sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:11.92,2:27:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}打包票{\r}\N- Damn sure.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:17.36,2:27:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}糖果园发生什么事？{\r}\N- What happened over in Candyland?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:19.44,2:27:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大火拼，主人中弹{\r}\N- Bunch-a shootin'. Massa got shot.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:23.00,2:27:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 谁射杀他？ - 德国人{\r}\N- Who shot him? - The German.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.20,2:27:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他为何杀他？{\r}\NWhy'd he do that?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:26.92,2:27:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑人和德国人装成奴隶商 但他们不是{\r}\NNigger and the German was actin' like they were slavers but they wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:30.88,2:27:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他们是什么？ - 赏金猎人{\r}\N- Well, what were they? - Bounty hunters.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:34.92,2:27:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我靠，罗伊，这可大条了{\r}\NFuck me, Roy. I mean, this could be big, mate.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:39.16,2:27:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑人，成交{\r}\NWell, smoke, you got a deal.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:44.00,2:27:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我还有个条件{\r}\N- I got one more condition.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:45.96,2:27:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}说吧{\r}\N- What's that?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:47.16,2:27:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们到那里时，时机来临时{\r}\NWhen we get there, when time come...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:52.16,2:27:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让我帮你们杀了他{\r}\N- ...you let me help you kill 'em. - Hey...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:55.24,2:27:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真有你的{\r}\Nyou're a funny bugger.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:57.00,2:27:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 松开他 - 好{\r}\N- Cut him loose. - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:59.80,2:28:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一言为定，黑人{\r}\NYou got yourself a deal, blackie.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:01.88,2:28:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一言为定，伙伴{\r}\NYou got yourself a deal, mate.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:03.80,2:28:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}喂{\r}\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:05.60,2:28:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}以黑人来说你挺不赖的{\r}\NYou're all right for a black fella. Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:13.76,2:28:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好了，伙伴{\r}\NThere we go. There you go, mate.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:15.68,2:28:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好{\r}\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:17.16,2:28:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那边的驮马给你{\r}\NWe're gonna give you that packhorse over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:19.96,2:28:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 鞍囊里装什么？ - 炸药{\r}\NWhat them saddlebags got in 'em?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:23.00,2:28:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}免谈，我才不骑背着炸药的马{\r}\N- Dynamite. - No. I ain't ridin' no horse with no goddamn dynamite on its back.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:26.36,2:28:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我能理解{\r}\NI can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:28.24,2:28:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}法兰基，让马卸下炸药棒{\r}\NFrankie, why don't you take them sticks off that horse
Dialogue: 0,2:28:31.40,2:28:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}插在黑鬼笼子上{\r}\Nand stick 'em in the nigger cage.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:34.68,2:28:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}来点炸药给你们黑鬼乐一下{\r}\NA little dynamite for you black fellas to play with.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:48.48,2:28:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}佛洛伊，马车上有枪吧？{\r}\NNow, Floyd, you got that rifle up on the wagon, don't ya?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:51.40,2:28:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对{\r}\NYeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:52.60,2:28:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把你的枪和枪套给他{\r}\NWhy don't you give him your gun and gun belt?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:55.20,2:28:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好{\r}\NRighto.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:56.72,2:28:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别摔到那玩意，好吗？{\r}\NNow, don't drop the fuckin' thing, all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:59.88,2:29:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我刚修好瞄准器，准得很{\r}\NI've just had the sights fixed and they're perfect.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:02.76,2:29:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}多谢告知{\r}\NOh, that's good to know.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:36.64,2:30:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把炸药丢给我{\r}\NThrow me up that dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:08.80,2:32:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 杰克 - 什么事？{\r}\N- Jake! - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:10.52,2:32:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快去看狗在鬼叫什么{\r}\NGet out there and see what's wrong with them goddamn dogs!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:15.88,2:32:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}干掉他们{\r}\NKill them
Dialogue: 0,2:32:18.56,2:32:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}杀了达太安，烂胚子{\r}\ND'Artagnan, motherfuckers!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:25.93,2:32:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:31.60,2:33:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}(12000元，凯文康迪）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:33:34.76,2:33:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（布希达冯夏夫）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:33:50.16,2:33:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再会了{\r}\NAuf Wiedersehen.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:52.08,2:34:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是我，宝贝{\r}\NIt's me, baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:41.76,2:35:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到那日，乐无比{\r}\NIn the sweet By-and-by
Dialogue: 0,2:35:50.48,2:35:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们会相聚{\r}\NWe will meet
Dialogue: 0,2:35:53.28,2:35:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在那美丽的岸边{\r}\NOn that beautiful shore
Dialogue: 0,2:35:59.47,2:36:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到那日 到那日{\r}\NBy-and-by By-and-by
Dialogue: 0,2:36:06.16,2:36:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到那日 乐无比{\r}\NBy-and-by We will meet
Dialogue: 0,2:36:10.48,2:36:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到那日，我们会相聚{\r}\N- We will meet by-and-by - Cora?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:12.60,2:36:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}柯拉，替大家准备一些咖啡{\r}\NWould you prepare us some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:15.92,2:36:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}夏芭，你帮她{\r}\NSheba, you help her.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:18.04,2:36:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}来吧{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:21.28,2:36:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}乐无比{\r}\NIn the sweet
Dialogue: 0,2:36:24.88,2:36:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到那日{\r}\NBy-and-by
Dialogue: 0,2:36:29.60,2:36:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们到那日都会跟凯文相聚{\r}\NOh, y'all gonna be together with Calvin in the by-and-by, all right.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:39.56,2:36:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只是比你们想像还早一点{\r}\NJust a bit sooner than y'all was expectin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:50.40,2:36:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}比利克莱许，我们进行到哪里？{\r}\NBilly Crash. Now, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:54.00,2:36:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想到了{\r}\NOh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:56.48,2:37:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上次见到你，你用脏手碰我那里{\r}\NLast time I seen you, you had your hands on my...
Dialogue: 0,2:37:10.88,2:37:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的妈呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:37:13.48,2:37:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}瘸哥，你这王八黑鬼{\r}\NDjango! You black son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:17.16,2:37:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是决哥，识相点{\r}\NThe D is silent, hillbilly.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:19.76,2:37:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不要！{\r}\NOh, no!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:23.00,2:37:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们这些黑人{\r}\NNow, all you black folks,
Dialogue: 0,2:37:25.80,2:37:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}建议你们远离这些白人{\r}\NI suggest you get away from all these white folks.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:30.24,2:37:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不行，史提芬{\r}\NNot you, Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:32.72,2:37:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你给我留下{\r}\NYou right where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:37.04,2:37:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}柯拉，你走之前 向拉拉小姐道别好吗？{\r}\NCora, before you go, will you tell Miss Lara goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,2:37:41.36,2:37:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么？{\r}\N- Do what now?
Dialogue: 0,2:37:43.04,2:37:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我说“向拉拉小姐道别”{\r}\N- I said, "Tell Miss Lara goodbye."
Dialogue: 0,2:37:48.00,2:37:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再见，拉拉小姐{\r}\NBye, Miss Lara.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:53.96,2:37:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们两个能闪人了{\r}\NY'all two run along now.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:14.00,2:38:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}史提芬，喜欢我这身新衣吗？{\r}\NStephen, how you like my new duds?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:19.04,2:38:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}之前我不晓得血红色跟我很搭{\r}\NYou know, before now I didn't know that burgundy was my color.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:33.28,2:38:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我数了发射六枪，黑人{\r}\NI count six shots, nigger.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:36.76,2:38:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我数有两支枪，黑人{\r}\NI count two guns, nigger.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:42.16,2:38:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你说76年来在这座庄园{\r}\NYou said in 76 years on this plantation,
Dialogue: 0,2:38:44.52,2:38:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你看过残害黑人的各种恶行{\r}\Nyou seen all manner-a shit done to niggers.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:47.40,2:38:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但我发现，你没提到击穿膝盖{\r}\NBut I notice, you didn't mention kneecappin'.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:50.84,2:38:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天啊！混蛋！可恶！{\r}\NOh, God! Motherfucker! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:54.32,2:38:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}76年，史提芬{\r}\NSeventy-six years, Stephen.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:56.16,2:38:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你看过多少黑人来来去去？ 7000个？{\r}\NHow many niggers you think you see come and go? Seven thousand?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:00.00,2:39:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}8000个？{\r}\NEight thousand?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:01.92,2:39:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}9000个？{\r}\NNine thousand?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:03.56,2:39:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}9999个？{\r}\NNine thousand, nine hundred and ninety-nine?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:06.44,2:39:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}凯文康迪嘴里吐出的每个字 全是狗屁倒灶{\r}\NEvery single word that came out of Calvin Candie's mouth was nothin'
Dialogue: 0,2:39:10.60,2:39:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但他说对一件事 我是万中选一的黑人{\r}\Nbut horseshit. I am that one nigger in 10,000.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:17.12,2:39:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你这王八蛋{\r}\NYou son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:20.16,2:39:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你这狗杂碎{\r}\NYou motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:22.12,2:39:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老天爷，让我杀了这黑人{\r}\NOh, sweet Jesus, let me kill this nigger!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:25.96,2:39:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不会全身而退的，决哥{\r}\NYou ain't gonna get away with this, Django!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:28.96,2:39:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们会逮捕你{\r}\NThey gonna catch your black ass.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:31.20,2:39:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你会出现在通缉令上{\r}\NYou gonna be on the wanted posters now, nigger.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:33.84,2:39:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}赏金猎人会追杀你{\r}\NThe bounty hunters gonna be lookin' for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:37.08,2:39:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你能逃走，但他们一定会揪出你{\r}\NYou can run, nigger, but they gonna find your ass!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:41.04,2:39:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到时候，天啊，看他们怎么搞你{\r}\NAnd when they do, oh, Lord, what they gonna do to your ass!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:45.36,2:39:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们不会轻易杀了你，你完蛋了{\r}\NThey ain't gonna just kill you, nigger! You done fucked up!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:50.08,2:39:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这座糖果园，黑人！ 你毁不了糖果园！{\r}\NThis Candyland, nigger! You can't destroy Candyland!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:55.08,2:39:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们就在这里，永远都有糖果园！{\r}\NWe been here! There's always gonna be a Candyland!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:09.88,2:40:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有黑人枪手能杀光全世界的白人{\r}\NCan't no nigger gunfighter kill all the white folks in the world!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:13.60,2:40:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们会揪出你{\r}\NThey gonna find your black ass!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:20.88,2:40:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}决哥{\r}\NDjango!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:23.44,2:40:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你这妄自尊大的…{\r}\NYou uppity son of a...
Dialogue: 0,2:41:00.56,2:41:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}嗨，小麻烦{\r}\NHey, Little Trouble Maker.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:02.64,2:41:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}嗨，大麻烦{\r}\NHey, Big Trouble Maker.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:32.00,2:41:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}知道江湖上会怎么称你？{\r}\NYou know what they are going to call you?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:34.52,2:41:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“南方第一快枪”{\r}\N"The fastest gun in the South."
Dialogue: 0,2:41:44.36,2:41:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们走吧{\r}\NLet's get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:14.76,2:45:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那个黑人是何方神圣？{\r}\NWho was that nigger?

